E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223984%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Cinderella's%20Castle%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67368630fa0140cdd563a3e4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECinderella's%20Castle%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World%20in%20Florida.%3Cp%3EArturo%20Holmes%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20Disney%20Dreamers%20Academy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDennis%20Speigel%2C%20founder%20of%20International%20Theme%20Park%20Services%2C%20Inc.%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Epic%20Universe's%20opening%20will%20likely%20bring%20more%20foot%20traffic%20to%20Central%20Florida%2C%20which%20can%20benefit%20the%20local%20attractions%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20length%20of%20stay%20for%20the%20tourists%20in%20Florida%20is%20going%20to%20increase%20dramatically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20people%20are%20going%20to%20load%20another%20day%20or%20a%20day%20and%20a%20half%20during%20their%20visit%20because%20there's%20more%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Disney%20and%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENBCUniversal%20first%20announced%20Epic%20Universe%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20new%20park%20represents%20the%20single-largest%20investment%20Comcast%20NBCUniversal%20has%20made%20in%20its%20theme%20park%20business%20and%20in%20Florida%20overall%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20L.%20Roberts%2C%20chief%20executive%20of%20Comcast%20Corporation%2C%20said%20in%20a%20press%20release.%20%26quot%3BIt%20reflects%20the%20tremendous%20excitement%20we%20have%20for%20the%20future%20of%20our%20theme%20park%20business%20and%20for%20our%20entire%20company's%20future%20in%20Florida.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Illustration%20of%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort's%20Epic%20Universe.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673685cbfa0140cdd563a3dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIllustration%20of%20Universal%20Orlando%20Resort's%20Epic%20Universe.%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Orlando%20Resort%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUniversal%20Orlando%20Resort%20was%20the%20company's%20oldest%20park%20in%201990%2C%20followed%20by%20Islands%20of%20Adventure%20in%201999%20and%20Volcano%20Bay%20in%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Epic%20Universe%2C%20guests%20will%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20explore%20five%20worlds%3A%20Super%20Nintendo%20World%2C%20The%20Ministry%20of%20Magic%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BHarry%20Potter%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20the%20Isle%20of%20Berk%20from%20the%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Train%20Your%20Dragon%26quot%3B%20franchise%2C%20Dark%20Universe%20featuring%20monsters%20from%20classic%20horror%20films%2C%20and%20Celestial%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Disney%20shocked%20fans%20in%20August%20when%20Experiences%20Chairman%20Josh%20D'Amaro%20said%20its%20parks%20were%20also%20expanding.%20The%20announcement%20came%20after%20the%20Central%20Florida%20Tourism%20Oversight%20District's%20board%20of%20supervisors%20approved%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdesantis-disney-development-deal-fifth-gate-new-theme-park-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2417%20billion%20development%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Disney%20two%20months%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Disney%20won't%20build%20a%20separate%20theme%20park%2C%20the%20entertainment%20giant%20will%20add%20new%20areas%20to%20its%20existing%20properties.%20Magic%20Kingdom%20will%20become%20home%20to%20a%20land%20dedicated%20to%20Disney%20villains%20and%20another%20based%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BCars%26quot%3B%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20Animal%20Kingdom%20will%20introduce%20a%20new%20land%20called%20Pueblo%20Esperan