%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmong%20them%2C%20the%20most%20prominent%20one%20was%20LABUBU%2C%20a%20small%20monster%20with%20high%2C%20pointed%20ears%20and%20serrated%20teeth%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20website%20said.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20a%20mischievous%20look%2C%20LABUBU%20is%20kind-hearted%20and%20always%20wants%20to%20help%2C%20but%20often%20accidentally%20achieves%20the%20opposite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20larger%20plush%20dolls%20from%20%26quot%3BThe%20Monsters%26quot%3B%20line%20are%20about%2015%20inches%20in%20height%20and%20cost%20about%20%2485.%20Smaller%20dolls%20cost%20between%20%2415%20and%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Pop%20Mart's%202024%20interim%20report%2C%20released%20on%20August%2020%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Monsters%26quot%3B%20line%20generated%20sales%20of%206.3%20billion%20Chinese%20yuan%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eor%20about%20%2487%20million%2C%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20company's%20stock%20is%20up%20nearly%20260%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20toy%20is%20so%20immensely%20popular%20that%20it%20sells%20out%20minutes%20after%20it's%20restocked.%20On%20a%20visit%20to%20a%20Pop%20Mart%20store%20in%20Singapore%2C%20a%20staff%20member%20told%20BI%20that%20Labubus%20are%20the%20most%20sellable%20figurines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20always%20out%20of%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Tony%20Lee%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20Pop%20Mart%20for%20four%20years.%20%26quot%3BEven%20when%20we%20replenish%2C%20within%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20or%20less%20than%20an%20hour%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20gone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Pop%20Mart%20typically%20restocks%20a%20few%20hundred%20figurines%20twice%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPop%20Mart%20doesn't%20announce%20when%20these%20restocks%20happen.%20Fans%20send%20updates%20to%20dedicated%20group%20chats%20on%20Telegram%2C%20and%20within%20less%20than%2030%20minutes%20of%20a%20restock%2C%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrazy%20line%26quot%3B%20forms%20outside%20t