s%20like%20Japan%2C%20Hong%20Kong%2C%20and%20South%20Korea%20is%20now%20spreading%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20Asia.%20Pop%20Mart%20has%20374%20outlets%20in%20China%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20getting%20really%20into%20'art%20toys'%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20kind%20of%20a%20mix%20of%20art%2C%20fashion%2C%20and%20pop%20culture%20all%20rolled%20into%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Kanaprach%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20a%20lot%20of%20millennials%20and%20Gen%20Zers%2C%20these%20aren't%20just%20toys.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThey're%20seen%20as%20little%20pieces%20of%20art%20or%20cool%20design%20items%20that%20look%20great%20in%20their%20homes.%20It's%20like%20adding%20a%20bit%20of%20personality%20and%20style%20to%20their%20space%2C%20not%20just%20something%20to%20play%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%2C%20a%20representative%20from%20Pop%20Mart%20said%20that%20Labubu%20has%20gained%20a%20strong%20global%20fan%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20become%20more%20than%20just%20a%20collectible%E2%80%94it's%20a%20way%20for%20people%20to%20express%20themselves%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237e61215-fe06-4fde-a209-d7d009d9b1f9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollectors%20say%20Labubu%20is%20worth%20the%20snaking%20lines%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Sim%20Pei%20Yi%20heard%20from%20a%20group%20chat%20that%20Labubu%20toys%20were%20being%20restocked%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20she%20rushed%20to%20a%20Singapore%20Pop%20Mart%20to%20join%20a%20snaking%20line%20with%20her%20colleague%20during%20lunchtime.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20'FOMO'%20feeling%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sim%2C%2031%2C%20who%20owns%20around%20six%20Labubu%20toys.%20%26quot%3BEverybody%20is%20getting%20Labubu.%20You%20will%20also%20want%20to%20have%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20girl%20holding%20her%20Labubu%20toys%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67331f17192f52589857c911%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAna%20Gonzales%20said%20she's%20spent%20around%20%24500%20on%20her%20Labubu%20collection.%3Cp%3EAna%20Gonzales%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElsewhere%20in%20Asia%2C%20Ana%20Gonzales%2C%2038%2C%20started%20collecting%20Labubus%20after%20her%20friends%20talked%20about%20it%20in%20a%20group%20chat.%20Labubu%20keyrings%20are%20difficult%20to%20get%20in%20the%20Philippines%2C%20so%20she%20buys%20%26quot%3Bblind%20boxes%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20toys%20that%20aren't%20labeled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGonzales%20estimates%20that%20she's%20spent%20around%20%24500%20on%20her%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20the%20real%20charm%20is%20in%20the%20blind%20boxes%E2%80%94not%20knowing%20what%20color%20you'll%20get%20adds%20so%20much%20excitement%2C%26quot%3B%20Gonzales%2C%20a%20social%20media%20manager%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BOpening%20a%20blind%20box%20after%20a%20long%20day%20or%20tiring%20week%20feels%20like%20unwrapping%20a%20gift%20to%20myself%20or%20a%20little%20reward.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20love%20for%20Labubu%20toys%20has%20also%20spread%20to%20the%20US%20market.%20In%20September%20last%20year%2C%20Pop%20Mart%20opened%20its%20first%20permanent%20store%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20Now%2C%20there%20are%2016%20Pop%20Mart%20stores%20nationwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETracy%20Hsu%2C%20a%2042-year-old%20housewife%20in%20California%2C%20learned%20about%20Labubu%20through%20Lisa%20%E2%80%94%20her%20favorite%20member%20of%20Black%20Pink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20first%20met%20Labubu%2C%20it%20made%20me%20really%20happy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hsu.%20She%20has%20around%2017%20Labubu%20toys%20and%20said%20she%20spent%20over%20%2410%2C000%20on%20them.%20Once%2C%20she%20even%20camped%20outside%20a%20Pop%20Mart%20store%20for%20the%20latest%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cim