s%20a%20bridesmaid%20for%20hire%20so%20that%20it%20wouldn't%20interfere%20with%20my%20full-time%20job%20during%20the%20week%20and%20brought%20in%20additional%20income%20through%20that%20stream.%20I%20also%20created%20profiles%20on%20babysitting%20websites%C2%A0and%20helped%20friends%20sell%20their%20clothes%20and%20furniture%20when%20they%20moved%2C%20and%20took%20a%20fee%20from%20sales%20that%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20shifting%20how%20I%20spent%20my%20weekends%2C%20from%20using%20the%20time%20to%20relax%20and%20socialize%20to%20finding%20ways%20to%20make%20money%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20earn%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20extra%20every%20month%20through%20various%20side%20hustles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20came%20in%20handy%20when%20I%20was%20laid%20off%20from%20my%20full-time%20job%20in%202015.%20When%20I%20lost%20that%20steady%20paycheck%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20up%20my%20wedding%20business%20and%20leverage%20some%20of%20the%20other%20side%20hustles%20to%20bring%20in%20more%20money%20than%20I%20was%20making%20from%20just%20the%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20make%20extra%20cash%20on%20the%20weekend%2C%20here%20are%20five%20side%20hustles%20you%20can%20try%20that%20may%20help%20you%20make%20more%20money%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Work%20events%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20steady%20work%2C%20grab%20a%20job%20in%20the%20event%20industry%2C%20since%20the%20weekends%20are%20when%20many%20people%20throw%20parties%2C%20celebrations%2C%20and%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20identify%20what%20skills%20you%20have%20that%20could%20be%20of%20value%20in%20the%20event%20industry.%20Use%20websites%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gigsalad.com%5C%22%3EGigSalad%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thumbtack.com%5C%22%3EThumbtack%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20browse%20common%20vendors%20that%20people%20hire%20for%20parties%20and%20see%20what%20passions%20you%20have%20that%20could%20be%20listed%20for%20hire%20on%20those%20types%20of%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20if%20you're%20someone%20with%20a%20passion%20or%20hobby%2C%20turn%20that%20into%20an%20offered%20service%20(floral%20design%2C%20DJ%2C%20photographer%2C%20etc.)%20or%20join%20an%20existing%20company%20that%20offers%20those%20services%20as%20their%20weekend%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20experience%20in%20the%20food%20services%20industry%20(as%20a%20server%20or%20a%20hostess)%2C%20you%20can%20also%20secure%20a%20job%20working%20for%20a%20caterer%20as%20a%20cater-waiter.%20These%20jobs%20typically%20pay%20hourly%20and%20are%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20house%20on%20a%20weekend%20and%20work%20as%20a%20food%20server%20at%20a%20big%20celebration.%20You%20can%20find%20a%20list%20of%20local%20opportunities%20on%20job%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Give%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20local%3Cstrong%3E%20tours%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20college%2C%20I%20took%20a%20weekend%20job%20as%20a%20campus%20tour%20guide.%20Each%20tour%20took%20around%20three%20hours%20and%20I'd%20start%20the%20week%20off%20with%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20in%20my%20pocket%20from%20that%20gig.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20extroverted%2C%20enjoy%20working%20with%20groups%20of%20people%2C%20and%20can%20retain%20information%20easily%2C%20you%20can%20find%20a%20weekend%20job%20as%20a%20local%20tour%20guide.%20Cities%20that%20are%20popular%20tourist%20destinations%20offer%20a%20variety%20of%20tours%20that%20focus%20on%20landmarks%2C%20food%2C%20famous%20TV%20shows%2C%20and%20more.%20You%20can%20browse%20local%20event%20websites%20to%20see%20what%20tours%20are%20offered%20and%20contact%20those%20companies%20to%20see%20if%20they%20are%20hiring%20tour%20assistants%20so%20you%20can%20get%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20consider%20creating%20profiles%20on%20websites%20that%20offer%20tourists%20tours%20by%20locals%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.toursbylocals.com%2F%3Fgclid%3DCj0KCQjwpv2TBhDoARIsALBnVnlRwIEcghbb92FiRvwWq-QbESwLM55PFuu9DIf-HxDti7kJoKbWi0MaAs9UEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETours%20By%20Locals%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.withlocals.com%2F%3Fgclid%3DCj0KCQjwpv2TBhDoARIsALBnVnkmNcEs0y__DzPaRLg___EcuXo-d0V7KvqA-XxtI-HnBsf9ZWcSnwYaAg3eEALw_wcB%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWith%20Locals%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20notice%20a%20specific%20kind%20of%20tour%20that%20you%20believe%20would%20attract%20customers%20on%20a%20weekend%2C%20consider%20starting%20it%20yourself.%20You%20can%20advertise%20your%20tour%20on%20websites%20that%20tourists%20visit%20to%20find%20local%20activities%2C%20like%20%3Cspan%3EAirbnb%20Experiences%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.yelp.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYelp%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20tour%20guide%2C%20your%20weekend%20pay%20can%20be%20determined%20by%20a%20variety%20of%20factors%2C%20including%20how%20many%20people%20take%20your%20tour%2C%20whether%20you're%20receiving%20an%20hourly%20salary%2C%20and%20how%20much%20cash%20you%20make%20in%20tips.%20If%20you%20run%20your%20own%20tour%20company%20and%20charge%20%2450%20a%20tour%2C%20you'd%20need%20to%20book%2020%20spots%20on%20Saturday%20and%2020%20on%20Sunday%20to%20make%20%242%2C000%20in%20potential%20profit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Help%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20with%3Cstrong%3E%20random%20tasks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%20early%2020s%2C%20when%20I%20wanted%20to%20make%20extra%20cash%20on%20the%20weekends%20but%20didn't%20want%20to%20commit%20to%20a%20regular%20job%2C%20I%20put%20myself%20on%20task-based%20websites%20where%20people%20could%20hire%20me%20for%20one-off%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20use%20websites%20like%20%3Cspan%3ETaskRabbit%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20Thumbtack%2C%20you%20can%20offer%20your%20time%2C%20resources%2C%20or%20skills%20to%20people%20who%20need%20them.%20In%20one%20weekend%2C%20you%20can%20help%20someone%20move%2C%20build%20their%20furniture%2C%20paint%20their%20apartment%2C%20or%20even%20take%20on%20tasks%20as%20their%20virtual%20assistant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20can%20make%20through%20this%20side%20hustle%20does%20vary%20based%20on%20how%20much%20you%20charge%20and%20how%20many%20hours%20on%20the%20weekend%20you%20work.%20However%2C%20you%20can%20set%20your%20rate%20for%20different%20tasks%20that%20you're%20willing%20to%20do%20or%20just%20set%20a%20general%20hourly%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Become%3Cstrong%3E%20a%20sitter%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20moved%20to%20New%20York%20City%20and%20needed%20to%20supplement%20my%20income%2C%20I%20took%20on%20weekend%20babysitting%20jobs.%20I%20created%20a%20profile%20on%20a%20local%20babysitting%20website%2C%20posted%20flyers%20in%20my%20apartment%20building%2C%20and%20shared%20the%20word%20with%20my%20friends.%20It%20helped%20me%20bring%20in%20an%20extra%20%241%2C000%20a%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20addition%20to%20babysitting%2C%20you%20can%20also%20get%20paid%20to%20house%20sit%20or%20pet%20sit%20for%20people%20when%20they%20go%20out%20of%20town.%20You%20can%20set%20up%20a%20profile%20on%20%3Cspan%3ERover%3C%2Fspan%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhousesitter.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHouse%20Sitter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20set%20your%20rate.%20If%20you're%20willing%20to%20let%20this%20side%20hustle%20carry%20over%20to%20during%20the%20week%20(especially%20if%20you%20work%20from%20home%20and%20can%20pet%20sit%20or%20house%20sit%20while%20working%20full-time)%2C%20you%20can%20really%20increase%20the%20amount%20of%20money%20you%20take%20in%20from%20these%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20like%20with%20other%20service-based%20side%20hustles%2C%20you%20can%20set%20your%20rate%20and%20the%20locations%20you're%20willing%20to%20travel%20to%20for%20potential%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Sell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20people's%3Cstrong%3E%20things%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20can%20look%20around%20their%20living%20spaces%20and%20find%20a%20collection%20of%20items%20that%20they%20are%20ready%20to%20part%20with.%20Rather%20than%20tossing%20old%20electronics%20in%20the%20trash%20or%20leaving%20unused%20furniture%20in%20the%20garage%20to%20collect%20dust%2C%20you%20can%20create%20a%20side%20hustle%20out%20of%20selling%20your%20own%2C%20or%20other%20people's%2C%20unwanted%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20times%20a%20year%2C%20I%20gather%20a%20pile%20of%20items%20around%20my%20house%20and%20list%20them%20for%20sale%20on%20places%20like%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20or%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.offerup.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOfferup%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20also%20take%20clothing%2C%20accessories%2C%20and%20shoes%20to%20local%20thrift%20stores.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20I%20have%20been%20able%20to%20make%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20off%20things%20around%20my%20house%20by%20doing%20very%20little%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20thing%20I%20always%20do%20is%20take%20inventory%20of%20what%20I%20want%20to%20sell%20by%20listing%20the%20proper%20name%20of%20the%20item%2C%20writing%20out%20a%20detailed%20description%2C%20and%20assigning%20it%20a%20price%20based%20on%20its%20retail%20value%20and%20condition.%20Then%2C%20I%20use%20my%20phone%20to%20take%20photos%20of%20the%20item%20from%20different%20angles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20list%20each%20item%20on%20multiple%20platforms%20to%20get%20the%20products%20in%20front%20of%20more%20people.%20Some%20items%20sell%20within%20a%20day%20or%20two%2C%20and%20others%20take%20months%3B%20it%20just%20depends%20on%20the%20supply%20and%20demand%20of%20what%20you're%20selling.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20really%20profit%20from%20this%20side%20hustle%2C%20offer%20to%20do%20this%20for%20other%20people%20so%20you%20have%20access%20to%20more%20items%20to%20list.%20Determine%20how%20much%20profit%20you'll%20take%20from%20each%20sale%2C%20and%20consider%20picking%20a%20specialty%20(like%20only%20selling%20electronics%20or%20furniture)%20so%20you%20can%20create%20a%20niche%20in%20the%20resale%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20May%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-thousands-simple-weekend-side-hustles-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731624961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62828be065d1770019e4883a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-thousands-simple-weekend-side-hustles-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you're%20looking%20to%20make%20some%20extra%20cash%20without%20taking%20on%20complex%20work%2C%20try%20taking%20on%20random%20tasks%20or%20selling%20other%20people's%20stuff%20online.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Jen%20Glantz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fearn-thousands-simple-weekend-side-hustles-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%225.6%20lakh%20Indians%20migrated%20to%20rich%20OECD%20countries%20in%202022%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731624496000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-115315388%2Cimgsize-586602.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2F5-6-lakh-indians-migrated-to-rich-oecd-countries-in-2022%2Farticleshow%2F115315069.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20record-breaking%205.6%20lakh%20Indians%20migrated%20to%20OECD%20countries