dicting%20the%20impact%20of%20the%20tax%20credits%20ending.%20%26quot%3BBut%20long%20term%20probably%20actually%20helps%20Tesla%2C%20would%20be%20my%20guess.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20that%20Trump%20plans%20to%20end%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%2C%20with%20support%20from%20Tesla%20representatives.%20In%20a%20related%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Musk%20called%20for%20an%20%26quot%3Bend%20all%20government%20subsidies%2C%20including%20those%20for%20EVs%2C%20oil%20and%20gas.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20had%20a%20longer%20time%20than%20some%20of%20its%20rivals%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-list-government-subsidies-tesla-billions-spacex-solarcity-2021-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebenefit%20from%20government%20subsidies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20market%20lead%20is%20well%20established%2C%20and%20it%20has%20led%20an%20EV%20pricing%20war%20that%20has%20squeezed%20its%20rivals%2C%20making%20it%20harder%20for%20them%20to%20survive%20if%20consumer%20demand%20falls%20even%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPut%20simply%3A%20Tesla%20wins%20if%20ending%20the%20tax%20credit%20pressures%20smaller%20rivals%20enough%20to%20stall%20their%20growth%20or%20even%20fold.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2291842e59-2373-4c08-abdd-17185b0bea0d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesla%20sells%20more%20EVs%20than%20anyone%20else%2C%20and%20more%20profitably%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20third%20quarter%20of%202024%2C%20Tesla%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdigitalassets.tesla.com%2Ftesla-contents%2Fimage%2Fupload%2FIR%2FTSLA-Q3-2024-Update.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20pre-tax%20profit%20margin%20of%2018%25%2C%20well%20above%20the%20industry%20average%20of%20around%209%25.%20Ford%2C%20the%20only%20competitor%20to%20break%20out%20its%20EV-specific%20finances%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fs201.q4cdn.com%2F693218008%2Ffiles%2Fdoc_financials%2F2024%2Fq3%2FPress-Release-Ford-2024-Q3-Earnings.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20-104%25%20margin%20for%20its%20Model%20e%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20many%20of%20Tesla's%20vehicles%20are%20also%20priced%20well%20below%20many%20competitors.%20The%20Model%203%20starts%20at%20%2442%2C490%20(after%20a%20cheaper%20option%20disappeared%20earlier%20this%20year).%20That's%20well%20below%20the%20average%20EV%20price%20in%20the%20US%2C%20which%20held%20steady%20at%20nearly%20%2457%2C000%20in%20October%2C%20according%20to%20Kelley%20Blue%20Book%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20juice%20sales%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftesla-can-make-cars-cheaper-than-competitors-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETesla%20has%20drastically%20cut%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20many%20of%20its%20cars%20over%20the%20past%20year%2C%20instigating%20an%20industry-wide%20price%20war%20that%20has%20cut%20into%20its%20own%20margin%20in%20pursuit%20of%20maintaining%20its%20industry-leading%20market%20share.%20Of%20the%20nearly%20600%2C000%20EVs%20sold%20in%20the%20US%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coxautoinc.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FQ2-2024-Kelley-Blue-Book-Electric-Vehicle-Sales-Report.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehalf%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20made%20by%20Tesla.%20Ford%2C%20in%20second%20place%2C%20accounted%20for%20just%20over%207%25%20of%20EVs%20sold%20in%20the%20same%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20losing%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20could%20also%20hurt%20some%20demand%20on%20the%20margins%20in%20the%20US%2C%20this%20will%20enable%20Tesla%20to%20further%20fend%20off%20competition%20from%20Detroit%20as%20pricing%2Fscale%2Fscope%20is%20an%20apples%20to%20oranges%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20auto%20industry%20once%20the%20EV%20tax%20credit%20disappears%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Ives%2C%20a%20longtime%20bullish%20analyst%20at%20Wedbush%2C%20told%20clients%20in%20a%20note%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c6cefac7-9186-47f8-8f0a-f2fb65808785%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETesla%20is%20ahead%20of%20the%20curve%20in%20building%20a%20US%20manufacturing%20presence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEliminating%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-state-electric-car-vehicle-tax-credits-rebates-qualify%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econsumer%20tax%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20part%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20would%20need%20congressional%20approval.%20It's%20not%20yet%20clear%20if%20Trump%20and%20the%20incoming%20Republican-controlled%20Congress%20would%20also%20target%20other%20IRA%20tax%20incentives%2C%20like%20those%20supporting%20domestic%20manufacturing%20of%20cars%2C%20batteries%2C%20and%20other%20components.%20Competitors%20like%20BMW%2C%20Honda%2C%20and%20Hyundai%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftechcrunch.com%2F2024%2F07%2F20%2Ftracking-the-ev-battery-factory-construction-boom-across-north-america%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eraced%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20scale%20up%20factories%20state-side%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20those%20credits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20has%20been%20ahead%20of%20this%20curve%20in%20manufacturing%2C%20too%2C%20with%20six%20US%20factories%20churning%20out%20cars%20and%20batteries.%20That%20work%20has%20paid%20off%2C%20and%20many%20Tesla%20models%20are%20regularly%20named%20as%20the%20most%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cars.com%2Famerican-made-index%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican-made%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20compared%20to%20competitors%2C%20many%20of%20which%20rely%20on%20factories%20in%20Mexico.%20In%20fact%2C%20only%20one%20other%20American%20automaker%20even%20cracked%20the%20top%2010%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETesla%20CFO%20Vaibhav%20Taneja%20said%20in%20a%20July%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20company%20has%20taken%20advantage%20o