%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227020dac3-e421-4813-8f06-665429e74373%5C%22%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20years%20of%20testing%20sous%20vide%20machines%2C%20I've%20found%20that%20one%20thing%20matters%20above%20all%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20finding%20a%20machine%20you'll%20want%20to%20cook%20with%3A%20ease%20of%20use.%20The%20simplest%2C%20most%20easy%20to%20use%20product%20we%20tested%20is%20the%20Anova%20Nano%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20better%20sous%20vide%20machine%20you%20can%20get%20at%20this%20price.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anova%20Nano%20isn't%20the%20fastest%20or%20most%20powerful%20machine%20we%20tested%3B%20it%20took%20almost%2020%20minutes%20to%20heat%20four%20quarts%20of%20water%20to%20130%20F.%20But%20for%20most%20home%20cooks%2C%20the%20%24100%2B%20price%20savings%20compared%20to%20more%20powerful%20machines%20are%20probably%20worth%20the%20extra%2010%20minutes%20you'll%20spend%20pre-heating%20the%20bath%20(a%20process%20that%20is%20totally%20hands-off).%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Anova%20Nano%20heating%20a%20pot%20of%20water%20on%20a%20butcher%20block%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67365abcfa0140cdd5638f34%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20slender%2C%20inexpensive%20machine%20has%20everything%20you'll%20want%20or%20need%20to%20get%20started%20with%20sous%20vide%20cooking%2C%20and%20is%20the%20best%20option%20for%20most%20home%20cooks.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20it%20lacks%20in%20power%20and%20speed%20it%20makes%20up%20for%20in%20effortless%20controls%2C%20accuracy%2C%20and%20usability.%20I%20didn't%20even%20need%20to%20read%20the%20instruction%20manual%20to%20get%20the%20Nano%20set%20up%20and%20cooking.%20The%20onboard%20controls%20are%20intuitive%20and%20it%20can%20be%20paired%20with%20Anova's%20app%20via%20Bluetooth.%20I%20found%20the%20Bluetooth%20connection%20to%20be%20much%20more%20stable%20and%20reliable%20than%20Anova's%20other%20sous%20vide%20machines%2C%20which%20pair%20via%20WiFi%20and%20seemed%20to%20frequently%20lose%20connection.%20That%20said%2C%20all%20the%20Anova%20machines%20use%20the%20same%20app%2C%20and%20I%20found%20it%20to%20be%20fairly%20buggy.%20Most%20folks%20will%20find%20the%20onboard%20controls%20easier%20to%20use.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c2aab61-ade7-43cd-bf00-10299f375342%5C%22%3EBest%20with%20an%20app%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'll%20be%20honest%3A%20the%20Joule%20is%20my%20personal%20favorite%20sous%20vide%20machine%20and%20a%20very%20close%20contender%20for%20our%20top%20pick.%20The%20only%20reason%20it%20was%20edged%20out%20by%20the%20Anova%20is%20because%20it%20lacks%20onboard%20controls%20and%20relies%20on%20an%20app%20for%20all%20functionality.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Joule%20has%20several%20features%20that%20distinguish%20it%20from%20the%20Anova.%20First%2C%20it's%20incredibly%20fast.%20In%20my%20tests%2C%20it%20was%20able%20to%20heat%20four%20quarts%20of%20water%20to%20130%20F%20in%20seven%20minutes%3B%20faster%20than%20any%20other%20machine%20in%20this%20guide.%20Second%2C%20it's%20the%20smallest%20of%20all%20the%20machines%20we%20tried%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20most%20versatile.%20It%20can%20work%20with%20a%20minimum%20of%201.5%20inches%20of%20water%20and%20a%20maximum%20of%208%20inches%2C%20so%20can%20be%20used%20in%20something%20as%20small%20as%20a%20coffee%20mug%20or%20as%20large%20as%20a%20cooler.%20I%20love%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20to%20break%20out%20the%20big%20Dutch%20oven%20every%20time%20I%20want%20to%20sous%20vide%20a%20couple%20of%20eggs.%20A%20magnetic%20bottom%20helps%20it%20stand%20in%20smaller%20metal%20pots%20for%20better%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20pot%20of%20water%20with%20ziplock%20bags%20filled%20with%20steak%20being%20heated%20by%20a%20Joule%20sous%20vide%20machine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67365bdcfa0140cdd5638fa9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20don't%20mind%20being%20tied%20to%20your%20phone%20or%20smart%20device%20to%20cook%2C%20the%20Joule%20could%20very%20well%20be%20the%20better%20option%20for%20you.%20Just%20don't%20rely%20on%20it's%20signature%20%26quot%3BTurbo%26quot%3B%20function.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20love%20the%20Joule%20app.%20It's%20the%20only%20app%20I%20tried%20as%20part%20of%20this%20testing%20that%20didn't%20give%20me%20trouble.%20It%20connected%20to%20the%20unit%20easily%20every%20time%2C%20gave%20clear%20and%20accurate%20alerts%2C%20and%20has%20a%20robust%20selection%20of%20recipes%20for%20getting%20started.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Joule%20recently%20got%20an%20upgrade%20in%20the%20form%20of%20its%20new%20%26quot%3BTurbo%26quot%3B%20version.%20This%20setting%2C%20controlled%20by%20the%20machine's%20phone%20app%2C%20aims%20to%20speed%20up%20notoriously%20sluggish%20sous%20vide%20cooking%20by%20heating%20the%20water%20bath%20to%20a%20slightly%20higher%20temperature%20than%20your%20desired%20doneness%20and%20then%20bringing%20it%20back%20down%20before%20your%20food%20can%20overcook.%20I%20tried%20it%20with%20strip%20steak%2C%20and%20I'm%20sorry%20to%20say%20that%20my%20desired%20medium-rare%20steaks%20came%20out%20completely%20boiled.%20I'd%20forgo%20this%20setting%20in%20place%20of%20manually%20selecting%20the%20time%20and%20temperature%20of%20your%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22113e0a3b-4d3c-43cb-9dd3-2bc4ff29cdb2%5C%22%3EBest%20for%20restaurants%20and%20pros%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESous%20vide%20is%20a%20popular%20restaurant%20cooking%20technique%20because%20it%20allows%20the%20chefs%20to%20hold%20large%20quantities%20of%20food%20at%20the%20perfect%20serving%20temperature%20without%20the%20risk%20of%20overcooking.%20For%20example%2C%20by%20holding%20steaks%20at%20125%20degrees%20F%20in%20a%20sous%20vide%20bath%2C%20a%20steakhouse%20can%20take%20each%20out%20as%20orders%20come%20in%2C%20give%20them%20a%20quick%20sear%2C%20and%20send%20off%20perfectly%20cooked%20steaks%20to%20diners%20in%20record%20time.%20It's%20a%20technique%20used%20in%20both%20Michelin-starred%20restaurants%20and%20chains%20like%20Starbucks%20and%20Chipotle.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20if%20you%20own%20or%20work%20in%20a%20restaurant%2C%20or%20are%20otherwise%20well-acquainted%20with%20sous%20vide%20cooking%2C%20I'm%20probably%20not%20telling%20you%20anything%20you%20don't%20already%20know.%20For%20restaurant%20folks%20and%20pros%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20something%20with%20more%20commercial%20features%20than%20the%20sous%20vide%20machines%20marketed%20for%20home%20cooks%2C%20I%20highly%20recommend%20the%20HydroPro.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22close%20up%20of%20the%20touchscreen%20on%20the%20breville%20polyscience%20hydropro%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67365dd7fa0140cdd5639065%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Breville%20Polyscience%20HydroPro%20is%20a%20powerful%20and%20thoughtfully%20designed%20choice%20for%20more%20experienced%20users%20or%20those%20working%20in%20a%20commercial%20setting.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20is%20thoughtfully%20designed%20for%20precision%20and%20repeatability.%20A%20touch%20screen%20lets%20you%20control%20time%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20flow%20rate%20(three%20speeds)%2C%20and%20offers%20a%20robust%20collection%20of%20built-in%20time%20and%20temperature%20algorithms%20for%20cooking%20and%20pasteurizing%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20foods%2C%20including%20grains%2C%20custards%2C%20and%20a%20whole%20host%20of%20meat%20cuts.%20You%20can%20save%20any%20settings%20in%20%26quot%3Bmy%20presets%26quot%3B%20right%20on%20the%20device%2C%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20repeat%20recipes%20night%20after%20night.%20The%20machine%20is%20ultra-accurate%20and%20fast%2C%20heating%20to%20130%20F%20in%20just%20eight%20minutes.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20adjustable%20flow%20settings%20were%20key%20when%20cooking%20eggs.%20I%20was%20able%20to%20lower%20the%20flow%20rate%20and%20angle%20the%20outport%20away%20from%20the%20eggs%20so%20none%20broke%20during%20cooking.%20The%20clamp%20is%20fully%20adjustable%2C%20the%20body%20comes%20apart%20for%20easy%20cleaning%2C%20and%20the%20machine%20can%20purportedly%20heat%20nearly%2012%20gallons%20of%20water%20when%20the%20bath%20is%20covered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226795e271-4397-46a2-ad30-e124be6160dc%5C%22%3EBest%20multitasking%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20usually%20skeptical%20of%20products%20that%20tack%20on%20sous%20vide%20settings%20to%20a%20completely%20different%20product%2C%20as%20I've%20found%20they%20usually%20don't%20have%20the%20precision%20temperature%20control%20needed%20for%20proper%20sous%20vide%2C%20but%20I%20was%20very%20pleasantly%20surprised%20by%20the%20InstantPot%20Duo%20Crisp.%20The%20machine%20reminds%20me%20a%20bit%20of%20traditional%20water%20ovens%20%E2%80%94%20the%20original%20sous%20vide%20machines%20before%20circulators%20came%20onto%20the%20market%20%E2%80%94%20which%20are%20essentially%20big%20heated%20boxes%20of%20water.%20Of%20course%2C%20the%20Duo%20Crisp%20also%20has%20the%20added%20benefit%20of%20multicooker%20functions%20like%20pressure%20cook%2C%20slow%20cook%2C%20sear%2C%20and%20even%20air%20fry.%20While%20I've%20tried%20all%20these%20settings%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20for%20this%20guide%2C%20I%20focused%20on%20how%20well%20it%20could%20sous%20vide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22various%20parts%20of%20the%20instant%20pot%20laid%20out%20on%20a%20kitchen%20table%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67365e20fa0140cdd5639082%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFor%20folks%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20trying%20sous%20vide%20but%20don't%20want%20to%20buy%20a%20dedicated%20machine%2C%20we%20recommend%20the%20InstantPot%20Duo%20Crisp%20%2B%20Air%20Fryer%2C%20which%20has%20a%20sous%20vide%20setting.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20machine%20took%20about%20a%20half%20hour%20to%20bring%20four%20quarts%20of%20room%20temperature%20water%20to%20both%20130%20and%20190%20degrees%20in%20separate%20tests%2C%20which%20was%20longer%20than%20other%20machines.%20However%2C%20the%20temperature%20was%20fairly%20accurate%20%E2%80%94%20only%201%20or%202%20degrees%20off%20from%20the%20target%20temperature%20at%20most%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20enough%20to%20impact%20the%20cook%20on%20most%20foods.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAside%20from%20the%20slow%20heating%20and%20the%20more%20limited%20capacity%20compared%20to%20versatile%20immersion%20circulators%2C%20I%20actually%20really%20liked%20using%20the%20InstantPot%20to%20sous%20vide.%20It's%20easy%20and%20intuitive%20to%20use%2C%20and%20makes%20for%20one%20less%20appliance%20I%20need%20in%20my%20house.%20If%20you're%20sous%20vide%20curious%20but%20not%20ready%20to%20invest%20in%20a%20dedicated%20machine%2C%20the%20InstantPot%20Duo%20Crisp%20is%20a%20great%20first%20step.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f8d82459-e8ec-4e12-b63e-11cb11bb99ef%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20sous%20vide%20machines%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22764%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20medium%20steak%20cooked%20using%20a%20sous%20vide%20machine%2C%20cut%20in%20half%20and%20sitting%20on%20a%20cutting%20board%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F673654a0ede4eeae3927a701%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22573%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%20addition%20to%20timing%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20for%20a%20sous%20vide%20machine%20to%20heat%20four%20quarts%20of%20water%2C%20we%20also%20look%20at%20how%20well%20it%20cooks%20eggs%20and%20steak.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20been%20testing%20and%20reviewing%20sous%20vide%20machines%20for%20seven%20years.%20During%20that%20time%2C%20I%20interviewed%20pioneers%20in%20sous%20vide%20cooking%20like%20Dave%20Arnold%2C%20Scott%20Heimendinger%2C%20and%20Tony%20Maws%2C%20and%20followed%20the%20growth%20of%20many%20brands%20in%20this%20guide%20since%20their%20startup%20phase%20and%20first-generation%20prototypes.%20My%20sous%20vide%20machine%20reviews%20and%20research%20on%20the%20history%20and%20safety%20of%20sous%20vide%20cooking%20have%20been%20published%20in%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%20sponsored%20nofollow%20sponsored%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-74273-20%26h%3Db80f89ec3e747c39c793e88819b355a0b957ccf587829f321b0b501c009e473c%26postID%3D67365321d4b5ffeb6fd6e43c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fkitchen%252Fbest-sous-vide-machine%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252Fgp%252Fproduct%252F1945256494%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESous%20Vide%20for%20Everybody%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20and%20Cook's%20Illustrated%20magazine.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20learned%20that%20the%20best%20sous%20vide%20machines%20excel%20at%20speed%2C%20accuracy%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20above%20all%20%E2%80%94%20ease%20of%20use.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20we%20tested%20seven%20sous%20vide%20machines%2C%20running%20each%20through%20a%20series%20of%20time%20and%20temperature%20tests%3B%20measuring%20fit%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20vessels%3B%20and%20evaluating%20ease%20of%20setup%2C%20use%2C%20and%20cleaning.%20We%20also%20cooked%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fanovaculinary.com%2Fquick-guide-to-cooking-sous-vide-eggs-with-anova%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E63%20C%20runny%20%26quot%3Bonsen%26quot%3B%20eggs%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20130%20F%20steaks%20with%20each%20machine.%20Here's%20the%20criteria%20we%20looked%20at%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpeed%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20timed%20how%20long%20it%20took%20each%20machine%20to%20heat%20four%20quarts%20of%20room%20temperature%20water%20to%20130%20F%20and%20190%20F.%20The%20best%20machines%20were%20able%20to%20do%20this%20in%20under%2010%20minutes%20and%20under%2025%20minutes%2C%20respectively.%20(It's%20worth%20noting%20that%20you%20can%20speed%20this%20process%20by%20covering%20the%20bath%20with%20plastic%20wrap%2C%20which%20we%20didn't%20for%20this%20test.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVersatility%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20good%20sous%20vide%20machine%20can%20be%20used%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20vessels%20to%20suit%20your%20needs.%20Models%20with%20a%20large%20range%20between%20minimum%20and%20maximum%20fill%20lines%20offered%20the%20most%20flexibility%20in%20this%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccuracy%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESous%20vide%20is%20a%20precision%20cooking%20technique%2C%20so%20accuracy%20is%20paramount.%20We%20regularly%20used%20a%20lab-calibrated%20thermometer%20to%20see%20if%20the%20actual%20temperature%20of%20the%20bath%20matched%20the%20temperature%20we%20set%20with%20the%20controls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEase%20of%20use%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESous%20vide%20is%20a%20somewhat%20niche%20cooking%20technique%2C%20so%20if%20your%20experience%20with%20it%20is%20frustrating%20or%20difficult%2C%20it's%20likely%20that%20your%20sous%20vide%20gear%20will%20end%20up%20in%20the%20donation%20pile.%20The%20best%20sous%20vide%20machines%20have%20bright%2C%20clear%20displays%3B%20are%20intuitive%20to%20operate%3B%20and%20easy%20to%20set%20up%2C%20clean%2C%20and%20store.%20We%20also%20looked%20at%20app%20connectivity%20for%20smart%20sous%20vide%20machines%2C%20though%20we%20ultimately%20prioritized%20models%20that%20have%20onboard%20controls%2C%20since%20they're%20the%20most%20user-friendly%20and%20versatile.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECooking%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOf%20course%20we%20looked%20at%20how%20well%20the%20machines%20cooked%20food.%20Generally%20speaking%2C%20if%20a%20sous%20vide%20machine%20is%20accurate%2C%20it'll%20cook%20just%20fine.%20But%20we%20also%20made%20eggs%20and%20steak%20with%20each%20machine%20to%20see%20if%20any%20machines%20had%20issues%20that%20impact%20cooking.%20The%20biggest%20issue%20we%20found%20was%20that%20machines%20with%20adjustable%20flow%20rates%20and%20outports%20were%20gentler%20on%20eggs%2C%20while%20machines%20without%20this%20feature%20often%20jostled%20eggs%20so%20much%20during%20cooking%20that%20they%20cracked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22215a6068-b0a7-4115-a375-de5eef87a19b%5C%22%3ESous%20vide%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20sous%20vide%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESous%20vide%20is%20a%20method%20of%20cooking%20food%20where%20the%20ingredients%20are%20sealed%20in%20plastic%20(though%20glass%20jars%20can%20be%20used%20for%20some%20applications)%20and%20immersed%20in%20a%20water%20bath%20set%20to%20(typically)%20the%20final%20cooking%20temperature%20of%20the%20food.%20As%20the%20sealed%20food%20sits%20in%20the%20bath%2C%20it%20slowly%20comes%20up%20to%20the%20correct%20internal%20temperature%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20danger%20of%20overcooking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20types%20of%20food%20can%20you%20sous%20vide%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESous%20vide%20cooking%20works%20best%20with%20meat%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20eggs.%20It%20particularly%20excels%20as%20a%20method%20of%20rendering%20tough%20cuts%20of%20meat%20juicy%20and%20tender%3B%20the%20low%20and%20slow%20temperatures%20allow%20tough%20collagen%20and%20fat%20to%20render%20slowly%20over%20many%20hours.%20Sous%20vide%20can%20also%20be%20used%20as%20a%20method%20of%20pasteurization%20for%20foods%20like%20eggs%20or%20homemade%20mayonnaise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EDo%20I%20need%20a%20vacuum%20sealer%20for%20sous%20vide%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENo.%20You%20can%20sous%20vide%20in%20any%20zipper-lock%20bag%20as%20long%20as%20you%20first%20remove%20the%20air.%20The%20easiest%20way%20to%20do%20this%20is%20place%20the%20food%20in%20the%20zipper-lock%20bag%2C%20press%20as%20much%20air%20out%20as%20you%20can%2C%20and%20then%20use%20the%20zipper-lock%20to%20seal%20all%20but%20a%20small%20corner%20of%20the%20bag.%20Slowly%20submerge%20the%20partially%20sealed%20bag%20in%20the%20water%20bath%20until%20all%20but%20the%20unsealed%20corner%20of%20the%20bag%20is%20submerged.%20The%20water%20will%20push%20out%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20air.%20Once%20the%20food%20appears%20tight%20against%20the%20bag%2C%20seal%20the%20final%20corner%20and%20drop%20the%20bag%20into%20the%20bath%20to%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20regularly%20sous%20vide%20large%20or%20irregularly-sized%20cuts%20of%20meat%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20purchase%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-vacuum-sealer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evacuum%20sealer%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20does%20a%20more%20complete%20job%20of%20removing%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20the%20advantages%20of%20sous%20vide%20cooking%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESous%20vide%20cooking%20offers%20the%20advantage%20of%20gradually%20and%20safely%20bringing%20your%20food%20to%20a%20designated%20cooking%20temperature%20while%20also%20keeping%20it%20from%20drying%20out.%20It%20takes%20a%20while%2C%20but%20it's%20almost%20foolproof.%20In%20the%20case%20of%20a%20cut%20of%20beef%2C%20all%20you%20have%20to%20do%20at%20the%20end%20is%20pull%20it%20out%2C%20give%20it%20a%20quick%2C%20hot%20sear%2C%20and%20you'll%20have%20an%20immaculately%20cooked%20steak%20right%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20are%20the%20disadvantages%20of%20sous%20vide%20cooking%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESous%20vide%20cooking%20takes%20a%20while%20(you%20should%20budget%20between%2020%20and%2030%20minutes%20for%20steak)%2C%20and%2