Satellites%2C%20How%20Farmers%20Time%20Crop-Burning%2C%20Scientist%20Explains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESince%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20north%20India%20has%20been%20covered%20in%20a%20thick%20blanket%20of%20smog%2C%20leading%20to%20low%20visibility%2C%20a%20drop%20in%20temperature%20and%20the%20air%20quality%20deteriorating%20to%20the%20'Severe'%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20quality%20remained%20a%20concern%20all%20over%20the%20Indo-Gangetic%20Plains%20(IGP)%2C%20with%20satellite%20images%20showing%20the%20alarming%20scale%20of%20the%20smog%20cover%20over%20northwest%20India%20including%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrap-3-in-delhi-enhanced-anti-pollution-measures-in-delhi-from-tomorrow-7019229%5C%22%3E%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20adjoining%20areas.%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20Delhi%2C%20parts%20of%20north%20Rajasthan%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttarakhand%2C%20are%20covered%20with%20smog.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHiren%20Jethwa%2C%20an%20aerosol%20remote%20sensing%20scientist%20at%20NASA%20Goddard%20Space%20Flight%20Center%2C%20shared%20the%20satellite%20images%2C%20detailing%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20smog%20covering%20the%20IGP%2C%20the%20reasons%20behind%20the%20dense%20smog%20in%20November%2C%20and%20how%20the%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%20are%20evading%20NASA%20satellites%20by%20burning%20crops%20late%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EEarly%20morning%20satellite%20images%20reveal%20IGP%20engulfed%20in%20smog.%20Delhi%20AQI%20in%20severe%20category.%20Urban%20heat%20island%20effect%20over%20Delhi.%20Farm%20fires%20in%20Pujab%20appear%20to%20have%20passed%20peak%20burning%20phase%2C%20but%20still%20plenty%20to%20fuel%20bad%20AQI%20downwind%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVishnuNDTV%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40VishnuNDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmohitk1%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40mohitk1%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBhattacharji%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CBhattacharji%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjksmith34%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40jksmith34%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FOTGXyJwVny%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FOTGXyJwVny%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Hiren%20Jethva%20(%40hjethva05)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhjethva05%2Fstatus%2F1856898440539656192%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThermal%20Inversion%20-%20A%20Key%20Factor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThermal%20inversion%20is%20a%20big%20factor%20behind%20the%20sudden%20spike%20in%20dense%20smog%20and%20pollution%20levels.%20Hiren%20Jethwa%2C%20a%20research%20scientist%20at%20NASA%2C%20explained%20the%20phenomena%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20warmer%20air%20sits%20above%20the%20cooler%20air%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20that%20does%20not%20allow%20the%20vertical%20mixing%20of%20pollutants%20and%20whatever%20we%20emit%20at%20the%20surface%20stays%20for%20around%20200%20metres%20within%20the%20boundary%20layer.%20The%20stronger%20the%20thermal%20inversion%2C%20the%20more%20pollutants%20will%20be%20trapped%20near%20the%20surface%20because%20there%20is%20no%20venting%20place%20for%20the%20pollutants%20to%20go%20up%20in%20the%20vertical%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20satellite%20images%2C%20we%20can%20notice%20that%20smoke%20from%20crop%20burning%20is%20mixed%20with%20clouds%20or%20is%20above%20them%20and%20that%20kind%20of%20situation%20furthers%20thermal%20inversion%20because%20of%20the%20absorption%20of%20light-absorbing%20aerosols%20and%20that%20it%20further%20warms%20the%20upper%20layer%20and%20increases%20thermal%20inversion%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Jethwa%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20fog%20occurrence%20over%20the%20Indo-Gangetic%20Plain%20(IGP)%20has%20increased%20and%20the%20occurrence%20has%20increased%20in%20November%2C%20which%20usually%20took%20place%20in%20December.%20He%20explained%20that%20there's%20more%20particulate%20matter%20(PM)%2C%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20cloud%20condensation%20nuclei%20which%20favours%20the%20formation%20of%20fog%20and%20when%20temperatures%20go%20down%20an%20enormous%20amount%20of%20aerosols%20contribute%20to%20fog%20formation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFarmers%20Avoiding%20NASA%20Satellites%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAQM%20appreciated%20Punjab%20for%20making%20strenuous%20efforts%20to%20bring%20down%20the%20stubble-burning%20count%20by%20nearly%2071%20per%20cent%20as%20compared%20to%20last%20year.%20Mr%20Jethwa%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20true%20that%20farm%20fires%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20have%20gone%20down.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20On%20Monday%2C%20farm%20fires%20in%20Punjab%20alone%20crossed%20the%207%2C000%20mark%20after%20over%20400%20fresh%20cases%20were%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethwa%20claimed%20that%20farmers%20in%20Punjab%20are%20timing%20crop%20burning%20with%20the%20overpass%20of%20NASA%20satellites.%20He%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20use%20the%20afternoon%20satellite%20overpass%20time%20data%20from%20NASA%20Satellites%20like%20Suomi%20NPP%20and%20Aqua.%20They%20overpass%20the%20region%20around%201%3A30-2%3A00%20pm%20but%20somehow%20they%20(farmers)%20have%20learnt%20that%20they%20can%20bypass%20the%20satellite%20overpass%20time%20and%20can%20burn%20the%20crop%20residue%20in%20the%20late%20afternoon.%20This%20is%20confirmed%20by%20the%20South%20Korean%20geostationary%20satellite%20that%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20crop%20burning%20happens%20after%202%20pm%20once%20the%20NASA%20satellites%20overpass%20the%20region%20when%20there%20is%20no%20surveillance%2C%20but%20the%20fires%20cannot%20be%20hidden%20from%20geostationary%20satellites%20which%20take%20a%20picture%20of%20the%20region%20every%20five%20minutes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethwa%20in%20an%20X%20post%2C%20shared%20satellite%20images%20from%20October%2029%2C%20taken%20by%20the%20GEO-KOMSAT%20A2%20satellite%2C%20shows%20a%20timelapse%20of%20the%20crop-burning%20activities%20in%20northwest%20India.%20The%20images%20show%20dense%20cloud%20cover%20over%20the%20region%20post-4%20pm%2C%20when%20compared%20to%201%3A30%20pm%2C%20suggesting%20that%20farmers%20are%20burning%20crops%20late%20afternoon%20to%20avoid%20NASA%20satellite%20surveillance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-conversation%3D%5C%22none%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EToday's%20GEO-KOMSAT%20A2%20satellite%20images%20visually%20convince%20of%20late%20afternoon%20burning%20acticitivities%20in%20NW%20India%2C%20avoiding%20NASA%20satellite%20surveillance%20around%201%3A30%20PM%20IST%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FVishnuNDTV%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40VishnuNDTV%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCBhattacharji%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40CBhattacharji%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fparthaabosu%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40parthaabosu%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjksmith34%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40jksmith34%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUrbanEmissions%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40UrbanEmissions%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Favoiland%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40avoiland%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmoesgoi%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40moesgoi%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FBJsidjNqzy%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FBJsidjNqzy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Hiren%20Jethva%20(%40hjethva05)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhjethva05%2Fstatus%2F1851270451709771888%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EOctober%2029%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20pollution%20loading%20in%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%20has%20reached%20the%20highest%20level%20that%20we%20haven't%20seen%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years...The%20crop%20burning%20has%20gone%20down%20over%20a%20certain%20period.%20Still%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20the%20geostationary%20images%2C%20there%20are%20many%20farm%20fires%20after%202%20pm%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20NDTV%20today%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20data%20from%20geostationary%20satellite%20is%20sensitive%20to%20the%20thermal%20signal%20produced%20by%20the%20fire.%20It%20lasts%20for%20at%20least%20four%20hours.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20whether%20there%20has%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20burnt%20area%2C%20Mr%20Jethwa%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20year%2C%20the%20data%20is%20yet%20to%20come%20out%2C%20but%20the%20fires%20seen%20so%20far%20until%20November%2014%20are%2019%25%20of%20the%20level%20seen%20in%202022%20and%2035%25%20seen%20in%202023.%20Of%20course%2C%20there%20is%20a%20drastic%20drop%20around%201%3A30%20p.m.%2C%20but%20if%20we%20see%20the%20burnt%20area%20data%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20drastic%20decrease.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%20the%20data%20showed%20that%20five%20farm%20fires%20were%20reported%20in%20Punjab%2C%2011%20in%20Haryana%2C%20and%20the%20highest%20number%2C%20202%2C%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20according%20to%20satellite%20data%20shared%20by%20the%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute%20(IARI).%20As%20per%20government%20data%2C%20Punjab%20recorded%2049%2C922%20farm%20fire%20events%20in%202022%2C%2071%2C304%20in%202021%2C%2076%2C590%20in%202020%2C%2055%2C210%20in%202019%20and%2050%2C590%20in%202018%20with%20many%20districts%20including%20Sangrur%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Bathinda%20and%20Amritsar%20witnessing%20a%20large%20number%20of%20stubble%20burning%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jethwa%20concluded%20by%20saying%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20farmers%20can%20hide%20the%20crop%20burning%20from%20the%201%3A30%20pm%20overpass%20time%20but%20the%20PM%202.5%20data%20and%20the%20pollution%20load%20over%20the%20Indo-Gangetic%20plain%20region%2C%20the%20geostationary%20satellite%20data%20and%20the%20burnt...everything%20is%20pointing%20toward%20fire%20is%20still%20present.%20Maybe%20it's%20still%20increasing...Smog%20towers%20are%20a%20small%20fix.%20It%20won't%20work%20unless%20we%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20crop%20burning%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EToxic%20Air%20In%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20factors%20contribute%20to%20pollution%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgrap-3-in-delhi-explained-what-is-banned-what-is-allowed-7019328%5C%22%3EDelhi-NCR%3C%2Fa%3E%20region%20including%20the%20emission%20of%20gases%20from%20vehicles%2C%20stubble%20burning%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20and%20construction%20and%20dumping%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20worsens%20every%20year%20after%20Diwali%20due%20to%20the%20bursting%20of%20firecrackers%2C%20which%20have%20been%20under%20a%20blanket%20ban%20in%20Delhi%20for%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20morning%2C%20dense%20smog%20caused%20zero%20visibility%20at%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20International%20Airport%20in%20Delhi%2C%20disrupting%20flight%20operations.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20Commission%20for%20Air%20Quality%20Management%20(CAQM)%2C%20the%20panel%20tasked%20with%20enforcing%20anti-pollution%20measures%20in%20Delhi-NCR%2C%20called%20it%20an%20%26quot%3Bepisodic%20event%26quot%3B%20and%20expected%20the%20situation%20to%20improve%20%26quot%3Bowing%20to%20stronger%20winds%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fbcibrj18_delhi-smog-cover_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20Delhi's%20Air%20Quality%20Index%20(AQI)%20was%20measured%20at%20428%20at%209%20am%2C%20placing%20it%20in%20the%20'severe'%20category.%20This%20marks%20Delhi's%20worst%20air%20quality%20reading%20of%20the%20season%20and%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20a%2024-hour%20AQI%20of%20418%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20an%20increase%20from%20334%20the%20day%20prior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vivek%20Nangia%2C%20a%20Pulmonology%20head%20at%20Max%20Hospital%2C%20told%20NDTV%20that%20%26quot%3BAir%20pollution%20has%20been%20labelled%20as%20the%20single-most%20hazardous%20environmental%20risk%20factor%20to%20our%20health.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLarge%20particulate%20matter%20of%205%20or%2010%20microns%20irritates%20the%20eyes%20and%20sore%20throat%2C%20but%20the%20smaller%20particles%20go%20inside%20the%20lungs%20and%20get%20absorbed%20into%20the%20bloodstream%20along%20with%20toxic%20gases%2C%20which%20results%20in%20an%20inflammatory%20cascade%20in%20the%20body.%20This%20is%20not%20only%20restricted%20to%20the%20lungs%20but%20the%20entire%20body.%20It%20could%20result%20in%20brain%20strokes%2C%20heart%20attacks%2C%20panic%20attacks%20and%20various%20types%20of%20cancer%2C%20a%20decreased%20life%20expectancy.%20For%20the%20lungs%2C%20it%20could%20cause%20illnesses%20like%20Asthma%20and%20even%20lung%20cancer%20which%20was%20earlier%20labelled%20as%20'smoker's%20cancer'.%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Nangia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3EThe%20satellite%20image%20shows%20the%20whole%20of%20Delhi%20and%20its%20adjoining%20areas%20covered%20under%20a%20dense%20layer%20of%20smog.%20The%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%20is%20better%20understood%20when%20the%20satellite%20picture%20is%20compared%20with%20an%20image%20from%20exactly%20one%20year%20ago.%20On%20November%2014%2C%202023%2C%20a%20less%20dense%20cloud%20cover%20was%20visible%20over%20the%20Indo-Gangetic%20plain%20from%20Punjab%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20On%20November%2014%2C%202024%2C%20the%20density%20of%20the%20smog%20cover%20appears%20to%20have%20doubled%20than%20what%20it%20was%20at%20the%20same%20time%20last%20year.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ffp3rv7q8_nasa-satellite-imagery_625x300_14_November_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CAQM%20has%20today%20enforced%20stricter%20norms%20to%20control%20air%20pollution%2C%20banning%20all%20non-essential%20construction%20demolition%20work%2C%20and%20plying%20of%20BS%20III%20petrol%20and%20BS-IV%20diesel%20cars%2C%20among%20other%20actions.%20The%20measures%20will%20be%20implemented%20from%208%20am%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20agreed%20to%20expedite%20a%20hearing%20on%20measures%20to%20combat%20the%20city's%20hazardous%20pollution%20levels%20on%20November%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESituation%20In%20Pakistan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20bad%20in%20neighbouring%20Pakistan%20too.%20Most%20outdoor%20activities%20have%20been%20banned%20in%20the%20Punjab%20province%20of%20the%20country%2C%20including%20an%20early%20shutdown%20of%20shops%2C%20markets%20and%20malls%20in%20some%20areas%20to%20curb%20pollution-caused%20illnesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDistricts%20of%20Lahore%2C%20Multan%2C%20Faisalabad%20and%20Gujranwala%20have%20reported%20an%20increase%20in%20patients%20with%20respiratory%20diseases%2C%20and%20eye%20and%20throat%20irritation.%20%26quot%3BThe%20spread%20of%20conjunctivitis%2F%20pink%20eye%20disease%20due%20to%20bacterial%20or%20viral%20infection%2C%20smoke%2C%20dust%