ckpoint%20during%20vehicle%20inspection%20on%20the%20Jharkhand-Bihar%20border%20in%20Giridih.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fvideo-rs-50-lakh-cash-found-stuffed-in-tyre-in-poll-bound-jharkhand-7021529%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Tribal%20Society%20And%20Pride%20Of%20Birsa%20Munda%3A%20Chhattisgarh%20Chief%20Minister%20Writes%20For%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20tribal%20society%20of%20India%20is%20rich%20in%20history%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20valour%2C%20with%20a%20legacy%20marked%20by%20struggle%20for%20identity%2C%20freedom%2C%20and%20dignity.%20This%20society%20has%20been%20fighting%20for%20its%20rights%20and%20freedom%20for%20centuries.%20The%20symbol%20of%20this%20wonderful%20heritage%20is%20Bhagwan%20Birsa%20Munda%2C%20who%20raised%20his%20voice%20against%20the%20exploitation%20of%20the%20tribal%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20in%20Ulihatu%20(now%20in%20Jharkhand)%20in%201875%2C%20Birsa%20Munda's%20life%2C%20struggle%2C%20and%20sacrifices%20for%20the%20preservation%20of%20tribal%20autonomy%20and%20culture%20are%20etched%20in%20the%20history%20of%20India.%20The%20struggle%20(Ulgulan)%20to%20save%20the%20tribal%20identity%2C%20autonomy%20and%20culture%20is%20unforgettable.%20Due%20to%20his%20contribution%20and%20sacrifice%20for%20the%20tribals%2C%20Birsa%20Munda%20is%20fondly%20called%20as%20%26quot%3BDharti%20Aaba%26quot%3B%20(God%20on%20Earth)%2C%20a%20symbol%20of%20respect%20and%20reverence%20towards%20him%20by%20the%20tribal%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBhagwan%20Birsa%20Munda%20dreamt%20of%20an%20exploitation-free%2C%20egalitarian%20society.%20Following%20his%20ideals%2C%20the%20state%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20constantly%20striving%20for%20the%20all-round%20development%20of%20the%20tribal%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20BJP%20government%20came%20to%20power%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20significant%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20towards%20the%20empowerment%20of%20the%20tribal%20community.%20Under%20the%20leadership%20of%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Atal%20Bihari%20Vajpayee%2C%20states%20like%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Jharkhand%20were%20formed%20so%20that%20tribal-dominated%20areas%20could%20be%20developed%20and%20their%20identity%20could%20be%20respected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20decision%20provided%20the%20tribal%20community%20an%20opportunity%20to%20preserve%20its%20traditions%20and%20cultural%20heritage.%20The%20ST%20Commission%20was%20made%20independent%20and%20empowered%20to%20bring%20the%20tribal%20community%20into%20the%20mainstream%20so%20that%20their%20voice%20could%20be%20heard%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20150th%20birth%20anniversary%2C%20it%20is%20a%20moment%20of%20immense%20pride%20that%20both%20the%20central%20and%20state%20governments%20are%20working%20relentlessly%20to%20turn%20his%20dreams%20into%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fuu1lc3ko_bhagwan-birsa-munda_625x300_14_November_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBirsa%20Munda%20aimed%20at%20empowering%20tribal%20communities.%20In%20line%20with%20this%20vision%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20launched%20several%20initiatives%20like%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Janjati%20Gaurav%20Yojana%20and%20the%20PM%20PVTG%20(Particularly%20Vulnerable%20Tribal%20Group)%20Vikas%20Mission%20to%20ensure%20the%20all-round%20development%20of%20tribal%20society.%20These%20schemes%20have%20been%20created%20to%20realise%20the%20overall%20development%20and%20self-reliance%20of%20the%20tribal%20society.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20recognition%20of%20the%20invaluable%20contributions%20of%20tribal%20heroes%20across%20the%20country%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20de