20Chanakya%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20there%20is%20his%20nephew%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bkingmaker%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20ruling%20alliance%2C%20Eknath%20Shinde's%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20eager%20to%20see%20its%20leader%20get%20the%20top%20job%20again%2C%20and%20many%20surveys%20have%20already%20declared%20him%20a%20popular%20leader.%20But%20that%20could%20prove%20insufficient%20should%20the%20Mahayuti%20win%2C%20with%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20and%20his%20supporters%20waiting%20in%20the%20wings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20June%202022%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis's%20supporters%20had%20been%20disgruntled%20over%20what%20they%20saw%20as%20short%20shrift%20to%20their%20leader%20despite%20the%20key%20role%20he%20played%20in%20steering%20the%20party%20back%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20had%20made%20his%20reluctance%20to%20accept%20the%20number%202%20position%20clear%20-%20he%20accepted%20only%20at%20the%20last%20minute%20after%20orders%20from%20the%20party%20high%20command.%20%C2%A0An%20extra%20chair%20had%20to%20be%20brought%20so%20he%20could%20join%20Mr%20Shinde%20on%20the%20dais%20for%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20at%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20there%20are%20whispers%20that%20the%20BJP's%20chief%20strategist%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20is%20garnering%20votes%20for%20Mr%20Fadnavis.%20At%20a%20recent%20public%20rally%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMaharashtra%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20faith%20in%20Modi%20ji%20and%20Fadnavis%20ji%26quot%3B.%20There%20was%20no%20mention%20of%20Eknath%20Shinde.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20real%20drama%20appears%20reserved%20for%20the%20Opposition%20MVA%20should%20it%20come%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20accused%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20of%20breaking%20the%20alliance%20with%20his%20steadfast%20demand%20for%20the%20top%20post.%20This%20time%2C%2