rl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmatt-gaetz-college-roommate-rumor-resurfaces-on-x-after-trump-names-him-as-attorney-general%2Farticleshow%2F115308149.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmatt-gaetz-college-roommate-rumor-resurfaces-on-x-after-trump-names-him-as-attorney-general%2Famp_articleshow%2F115308149.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fmatt-gaetz-college-roommate-rumor-resurfaces-on-x-after-trump-names-him-as-attorney-general%2Famp_articleshow%2F115308149.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Key%20Bangladesh%20Official%20Proposes%20Removing%20'Secularism'%20From%20Constitution%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBangladesh's%20top%20legal%20official%20has%20proposed%20to%20remove%20the%20words%20%26quot%3Bsecularism%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsocialism%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20Constitution%20apart%20from%20a%20provision%20prescribing%20capital%20punishment%20for%20regime%20change%20through%20extra-constitutional%20means.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%20in%20the%20High%20Court%20during%20a%20hearing%20on%20a%20writ%20petition%20filed%20by%20a%20group%20of%20citizens%2C%20Attorney%20General%20Mohammad%20Asazzaman%20on%20Wednesday%20sought%20to%20remove%20%26quot%3Bsecularism%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bsocialism%26quot%3B%20as%20two%20of%20the%20four%20principles%20of%20the%20Constitution%20alongside%20the%20designation%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20as%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20was%20the%20undisputed%20leader%20of%20Bangladesh%20but%20the%20Awami%20League%20politicised%20him%20in%20the%20party's%20interest%2C%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20founding%20leader%20of%20Bangladesh%20who%20is%20popularly%20known%20as%20Bangabandhu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20writ%20petition%20challenged%20the%20validity%20of%20the%20Constitution's%2015th%20amendment%20made%20by%20the%20now-ousted%20Awami%20League%20regime%20of%20deposed%20prime%20minister%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20in%202011%20while%20a%20two-judge%20High%20Court%20bench%20issued%20a%20rule%20asking%20the%20interim%20government%20to%20come%20up%20with%20its%20stance%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20whole%2C%20we%20do%20not%20want%20that%20(HC)%20rule%20to%20be%20scrapped%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20attorney%20general%20said%2C%20clarifying%20the%20government's%20stance%20on%20the%20writ%20petition%20while%20talking%20to%20newsmen%20at%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20people%2C%20mostly%20lawyers%2C%20emerged%20as%20interveners%20in%20the%20writ%20petition%2C%20some%20supporting%20the%20plea%20and%20some%20opposing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2015th%20amendment%20was%20passed%20in%20parliament%20with%20the%20strength%20of%20a%20brute%20majority%20of%20the%20Awami%20League%2C%20restoring%2C%20inserting%20and%20scrapping%20several%20provisions%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendments%20included%20the%20restoration%20of%20secularism%20as%20a%20state%20principle%2C%20the%20scrapping%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20system%20for%20election%20oversight%2C%20assuming%20state%20power%20through%20extra-constitutional%20means%20and%20the%20designating%20of%20Sheikh%20Mujibur%20Rahman%20as%20the%20Father%20of%20the%20Nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20concluding%20arguments%2C%20Asaduzzaman%20told%20the%20court%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20wanted%20to%20declare%20the%2015th%20amendment%20to%20the%20Constitution%20largely%20unconstitutional%2C%20retaining%20only%20select%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20particularly%20demanded%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20system%20and%20the%20provision%20of%20the%20referendum%20in%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Awami%20League%20regime%20was%20toppled%20on%20August%205%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20mass%20upsurge%20originating%20from%20a%20quota%20reform%20campaign%20by%20the%20Anti-Discrimination%20Students%20Movement.%20Three%20days%20later%20Nobel%20laureate%20Muhammad%20assumed%20office%20as%20the%20chief%20adviser%20of%20the%20interim%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%20general%20criticised%20Article%207A%20inserted%20under%20the%2015th%20amendment%20that%20criminalises%20any%20attempt%20to%20repeal%2C%20suspend%2C%20or%20subvert%20the%20Constitution%20through%20force%20or%20unconstitutional%20means%2C%20calling%20such%20acts%20as%20sedition%2C%20which%20are%20punishable%20with%20the%20death%20penalty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20this%20restriction%20limits%20democratic%20change%20and%20disregards%20the%20recent%20mass%20uprising%20that%20deposed%20the%20Awami%20League%20government%20and%20demanded%20the%20restoration%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20(provisions%20of%20the%2015th)%20amendment%20betrays%20the%20sacrifices%20of%20martyrs%20like%20Abu%20Sayed%20and%20Mugdho%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Asaduzzaman%2C%20referring%20to%20two%20students%20who%20were%20shot%20dead%20during%20the%20July-August%20mass%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsaduzzaman%20was%20appointed%20as%20the%20attorney%20general%20days%20after%20the%20ouster%20of%20the%20past%20regime%20and%20the%20resignation%20of%20his%20predecessor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731604740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fsct30qqg_bangladesh-crisis-_625x300_05_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbangladesh-attorney-general-mohammad-asazzama-proposes-removing-secularism-socialism-from-constitution-7021177%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bangladesh's%20top%20le