w%2F115307906.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115307906.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ERenowned%20singer%20B%20Praak%2C%20in%20a%20heartfelt%20interview%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20the%20devastating%20loss%20of%20his%20newborn%20son%2C%20Fazza.%20He%20emotionally%20described%20the%20unbearable%20pain%20of%20losing%20a%20child%2C%20comparing%20it%20to%20carrying%20the%20heaviest%20weight%20imaginable.%20Praak%20also%20revealed%20the%20lingering%20pain%20his%20wife%2C%20Meera%20Bachan%2C%20carries%2C%20expressing%20her%20wish%20to%20have%20seen%20their%20son%20one%20last%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fmusic%2Fnews%2Fb-praak-breaks-down-talking-about-the-passing-away-of-his-newborn-son-i-never-carried-this-much-weight-in-my-life%2Farticleshow%2F115307906.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20Tests%20Latest%20Pinaka%20System%20As%20France%2C%20Armenia%20Line-Up%20To%20Buy%20Rockets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20a%20rise%20in%20global%20demand%20for%20it%2C%20India%20today%20successfully%20completed%20the%20flight-test%20of%20its%20advanced%20guided%20weapon%20system%20Pinaka.%20During%20the%20test%2C%20the%20Pinaka%20system's%20range%2C%20accuracy%2C%20consistency%20and%20rate%20of%20fire%20for%20multiple%20target%20engagement%20in%20a%20salvo%20mode%20were%20assessed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefence%20Research%20and%20Development%20Organisation%20or%20DRDO%20has%20successfully%20completed%20the%20flight-tests%20of%20Guided%20Pinaka%20Weapon%20System%20as%20part%20of%20Provisional%20Staff%20Qualitative%20Requirements%20(PSQR)%20validation%20trials%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Defence%20Ministry%20said%20today%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20flight-tests%20have%20been%20conducted%20in%20three%20phases%20at%20different%20field%20firing%20ranges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwelve%20rockets%20from%20each%20production%20agency%20from%20two%20in-service%20Pinaka%20launchers%20upgraded%20by%20the%20launcher%20production%20agencies%20have%20been%20tested%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%2C%20New%20Delhi's%20defence%20manufacturing%20push%20under%20'Make%20in%20India'%20is%20gaining%20momentum.%20France%20has%20recently%20showed%20interest%20in%20the%20Pinaka%20Multi-Barrel%20Rocket%20Launcher%20or%20MBRL%20system%20to%20bolster%20its%20defences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETHE%20PINAKA%20SYSTEM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pinaka%20system%2C%20considered%20on%20par%20with%20America's%20HIMARS%20system%2C%20has%20been%20India's%20first%20major%20defence%20export%20as%20conflict-hit%20Armenia%20had%20placed%20the%20first%20order.%20Now%20France%20has%20also%20shown%20interest%20in%20the%20advanced%20rocket%20system%20to%20boost%20its%20army's%20artillery%20division.%20In%20fact%2C%20talks%20are%20already%20at%20a%20fairly%20advanced%20stage%2C%20sources%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20France%20has%20decided%20to%20test%20the%20system%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamed%20after%20Lord%20Shiva's%20divine%20bow%2C%20the%20Pinaka%20rocket%20system%20was%20a%20replacement%20for%20the%20Russian%20Grad%20BM-21%20rocket%20launcher%20for%20the%20Indian%20Army.%20It%20was%20first%20deployed%20during%20the%201999%20Kargil%20War.%20The%20Pinaka%20system%20had%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20destroying%20Pakistani%20positions%20at%20strategic%20heights%20during%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pinaka%20rocket%20system%20is%20developed%20by%20Armament%20Research%20%26amp%3B%20Development%20Establishment%20or%20ARDE%2C%20which%20comes%20under%20the%20DRDO.%20The%20system%20comprises%20of%20a%20free-flight%20artillery%20rocket%20having%20a%20maximum%20range%20of%2038%20km%20with%20different%20types%20of%20warheads%20and%20fuzes.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20multi-tube%20launcher%20vehicle%2C%20a%20replenishment-cum-loader%20vehicle%2C%20a%20replenishment%20vehicle%2C%20and%20a%20command%20post%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20multi-barrel%20rocket%20system%20has%20two%20pods%20containing%206%20rockets%20each%2C%20capable%20of%20firing%20all%2012%20rockets%20in%20salvo%20mode%20within%2044%20seconds%2C%20neutralizing%20a%20target%20area%20of%20700%20x%20500%20meters.%20For%20the%20Indian%20Army's%20specific%20requirement%20of%20a%20free%20flight%20rocket%20with%20enhanced%20range%2C%20ARDE%20has%20successfully%20developed%20the%20Pinaka%20Mk-II%20rocket%20with%20a%2060-km%20range.%20The%20existing%20launch%20vehicle%20and%20ground%20systems%20of%20Pinaka%20MBRS%20is%20used%20for%20the%20Mk-II%20as%20well%2C%20with%20minor%20modifications%20for%20firing%20this%20new%20rocket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20battery%20can%20fire%2072%20rockets.%20Each%20launcher%20can%20now%20be%20operated%20independently%20and%20rockets%20can%20be%20fired%20individually%20or%20simultaneously%20in%20different%20directions.%20The%20launcher%20may%20be%20operated%20in%20manual%2C%20remote%2C%20stand%20alone%2C%20and%20autonomous%20modes.%20Its%20shoot-and-scoot%20capabilities%20also%20enable%20it%20to%20escape%20counter%20battery%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20version%20of%20the%20Pinaka%20system%20is%20a%20guided%20one%2C%20which%20means%20that%20the%20rockets%20have%20seekers%2C%20which%20are%20used%20for%20precision%20strikes.%20Because%20of%20it%20becoming%20a%20guided%20system%2C%20it%20has%20now%20been%20able%20to%20increase%20its%20range%20to%20nearly%20double%20of%20what%20the%20first%20version%20was.%20The%20DRDO%20is%20now%20working%20on%20a%20guided%20Pinaka%20system%20which%20is%20capable%20of%20ranges%20greater%20than%20120%20km%2C%20150%20km%2C%20and%20200%20km%20to%20counter%20China's%20long-range%20guided%20rocket%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGLOBAL%20INTEREST%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20is%20already%20in%20service%20with%20the%20Indian%20Army%20and%20deployed%20both%20at%20the%20LoC%20with%20Pakistan%20and%20LAC%20with%20China.%20It%20was%20also%20reportedly%20delivered%20to%20Armenia%20via%20Iran%20in%202023%20to%20bolster%20its%20defence%20against%20Azerbaijan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrance's%20move%20to%20consider%20buying%20the%20Pinaka%20system%20is%20part%20of%20the%20effort%20to%20boost%20defence%20and%20strategic%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations.%20France%20is%20India's%20second%20biggest%20defence%20supplier%20after%20Russia.%20The%20recent%20T%20AC%20295%20transport%20aircraft%20deal%20and%20the%20Rafael%20deal%20are%20testament%20to%20Paris%20and%20New%20Delhi's%20steadfast%20defence%20ties.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731604080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-12%2Fj9crr3d8_pinaka-extended-range-multi-barrel-rocket-launcher-system-pti-photo_625x300_11_December_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpinaka-mbrl-system-latest-pinaka-system-tested-as-france-armenia-line-up-to-buy-indian-rockets-7020634%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20a%20rise%20in%20global%20demand%20for%20it%2C%20India%20today%20successfully%20completed%20the%20flight-test%20of%20its%20advanced%20guided%20weapon%20system%20Pinaka.%20During%20the%20test%2C%20the%20Pinaka%20system's%20range%2C%20accuracy%2C%20consistency%20and%20rate%20of%20fire%20were%20assessed.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpinaka-mbrl-system-latest-pinaka-system-tested-as-france-armenia-line-up-to-buy-indian-rockets-7020634%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Police%20find%20up%20to%2020%20human%20skulls%20in%20New%20Mexico%20residence%2C%20lin