20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20the%20Women%20and%20Family%20Department%20of%20the%20Tehran%20Headquarters%20for%20the%20Promotion%20of%20Virtue%20and%20Prevention%20of%20Vice%20falls%20under%20the%20direct%20authority%20of%20Iran's%20supreme%20leader%20Ali%20Khamenei.%20The%20body%20is%20reportedly%20responsible%20for%20defining%20and%20enforcing%20strict%20religious%20standards%20in%20Iran%2C%20particularly%20those%20related%20to%20women's%20dress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMove%20Sparks%20Outrage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20came%20weeks%20after%20a%20university%20student%2C%20who%20stripped%20down%20to%20her%20underwear%20on%20a%20Tehran%20campus%20in%20an%20apparent%20protest%20at%20harsh%20treatment%20by%20dress%20code%20enforcers%2C%20was%20detained%20and%20sent%20to%20a%20psychiatric%20hospital%20for%20mental%20health%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20news%20of%20the%20new%20clinic%20has%20spread%20among%20the%20%26quot%3BWoman%2C%20Life%2C%20Freedom%26quot%3B%20protest%20groups%20and%20women%2C%20sparking%20fear%20and%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20The%20Guardian%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20a%20young%20woman%20from%20Iran%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20won't%20be%20a%20clinic%2C%20it%20will%20be%20a%20prison.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20struggling%20to%20make%20ends%20meet%20and%20have%20power%20outages%2C%20but%20a%20piece%20of%20cloth%20is%20what%20this%20state%20is%20worried%20about.%20If%20there%20was%20a%20time%20for%20all%20of%20us%20to%20come%20back%20to%20the%20streets%2C%20it's%20now%20or%20they'll%20lock%20us%20all%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Iranian%20human%20rights%20lawyer%2C%20Hossein%20Raeesi%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20clinic%20to%20treat%20women%20who%20did%20not%20comply%20with%20hijab%20laws%20is%20%26quot%3Bneither%20Islamic%20nor%20aligned%20with%20Iranian%20law%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EUse%20Of%20Psychiatric%20Facilities%20To%20Curb%20Dissent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIranian%20authorities%20have%20been%20widely%20accused%20of%20using%20mental%20health%20institutions%20to%20curb%20the%20dissent%20against%20the%20strict%20hijab%20law.%20The%20method%20has%20been%20condemned%20by%20human%20rights%20advocates%20as%20psychologically%20abusive%20and%20manipulative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fglobal-development%2F2024%2Fnov%2F14%2Firan-announces-treatment-clinic-for-women-who-defy-strict-hijab-laws%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sima%20Sabet%2C%20a%20UK-based%20Iranian%20journalist%20who%20was%20a%20target%20of%20an%20Iranian%20assassination%20attempt%20last%20year%2C%20said%20the%20move%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshameful%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20of%20establishing%20clinics%20to%20%E2%80%98cure'%20unveiled%20women%20is%20chilling%2C%20where%20people%20are%20separated%20from%20society%20simply%20for%20not%20conforming%20to%20the%20ruling%20ideology%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20%26quot%3BWoman%2C%20Life%2C%20Freedom%26quot%3B%20movement%20began%2C%20hardliners%20have%20increased%20efforts%20to%20enforce%20strict%20dress%20codes%20for%20women.%20Artists%2C%20including%20actresses%20Afsaneh%20Bayegan%2C%20Azadeh%20Samadi%2C%20and%20Leila%20Bolukat%2C%20who%20posted%20images%20of%20themselves%20without%20a%20hijab%2C%20reportedly%20received%20court-ordered%20mandates%20for%20weekly%20visits%20to%20psychological%20centers%20for%20mental%20health%20certificates%20in%20response%20to%20their%20conduct.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%C2%A0%26quot%3BWoman%2C%20Life%2C%20Freedom%26quot%3B%20movement%20began%20in%20Iran%20after%20the%20death%20of%20young%20woman%20Mahsa%20Amini%20in%20police%20custody%20over%20hijab%20violations%20in%20Sep