wed%20on%20the%20roads%20in%20Delhi%20and%20parts%20of%20the%20National%20Capital%20Region%20(NCR)%20such%20as%20Gurugram%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Faridabad%2C%20and%20Gautam%20Budh%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20rising%20pollution%20levels%2C%20all%20primary%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20be%20shifting%20to%20online%20classes%2C%20until%20further%20directions%2C%26quot%3B%20Atishi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EDue%20to%20rising%20pollution%20levels%2C%20all%20primary%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20be%20shifting%20to%20online%20classes%2C%20until%20further%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Atishi%20(%40AtishiAAP)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FAtishiAAP%2Fstatus%2F1857074637743464893%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi's%20AQI%20at%209%20am%20today%20was%20in%20'severe'%20category%2C%20with%20a%20reading%20of%20428.%20On%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20city%20reported%20the%20worst%20AQI%20in%20the%20country%2C%20with%20air%20quality%20turning%20'severe'%20for%20the%20first%20time%20this%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDoctors%20have%20cautioned%20people%20to%20stay%20indoors%20as%20much%20as%20possible.%20The%20effects%20of%20severe%20air%20pollution%20is%20not%20only%20limited%20to%20physical%20health%2C%20but%20also%20extended%20to%20cognitive%20wellbeing%2C%20affecting%20mood%20and%20emotional%20resilience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Arunesh%20Kumar%2C%20a%20senior%20consultant%20on%20respiratory%20medicine%20at%20Paras%20Health%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20said%20people%20need%20to%20limit%20outdoor%20activities%2C%20especially%20during%20early%20morning%20and%20late%20evening%20when%20air%20quality%20is%20typically%20poor%2C%20to%20protect%20the%20body%20from%20the%20impact%20of%20pollution%20post-festive%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20going%20outside%20is%20necessary%2C%20wearing%20an%20N95%20mask%20can%20help%20filter%20harmful%20particles.%20Indoors%2C%20using%20a%20HEPA%20air%20purifier%20is%20recommended%20as%20it%20can%20significantly%20reduce%20particulate%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kumar%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731598260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fl12vdl7o_delhi-smog_625x300_13_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprimary-schools-in-delhi-to-shift-to-online-classes-amid-severe-pollution-says-chief-minister-atishi-7020339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Primary%20schools%20in%20Delhi%20will%20switch%20to%20online%20learning%20mode%20from%20Friday%20due%20to%20severe%20air%20pollution%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Atishi%20announced%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fprimary-schools-in-delhi-to-shift-to-online-classes-amid-severe-pollution-says-chief-minister-atishi-7020339%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EaseMyTrip%20Q2FY25%20results%3A%20Net%20profit%20declines%2045%25%20to%20Rs%2026%20crore%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731596985000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Feasemytrip-q2fy25-results-net-profit-declines-45-to-rs-26-crore-124111401920_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi-headquartered%20company's%20gross%20booking%20revenue%20(GBR)%20from%20hotels%20and%20packages%20reached%20Rs%202%2C414%20million%2C%20marking%20a%20178.4%20per%20cent%20Y-o-Y%20growth%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Champions%20Trophy%20Row%3A%20PCB%20vs%20BCCI%20Battle%20Leaves%20ICC%20With%20Only%203%20Options%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20finds%20itself%20in%20a%20precarious%20situation%20over%20next%20year's%20Champions%20Trophy.%20The%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20has%20already%20shut%20down%20the%20idea%20of%20sending%20the%20Indian%20men's%20cricket%20team%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20event%2C%20leaving%20the%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20fuming.%20PCB%2C%20who%20have%20the%20legal%20hosting%20rights%20for%20the%20event%2C%20isn't%20willing%20to%20settle%20for%20a%20hybrid%20system%20once%20again%2C%20having%20done%20so%20on%20multiple%20occasions%20before.%20The%20situation%2C%20hence%2C%20puts%20the%20onus%20on%20ICC%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20neither%20the%20PCB%20nor%20the%20BCCI%20are%20willing%20to%20hedge%20from%20their%20current%20stance%2C%20the%20responsibility%20of%20resolving%20the%20matter%20falls%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20ICC%2C%20who%20only%20have%20three%20options%20with%20them.%20They%20are%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Convince%20the%20PCB%20to%20agree%20on%20BCCI's%20hybrid%20model%20proposal%2C%20which%20would%20see%20five%20of%20the%2015%20games%20of%20the%20tournament%20being%20played%20in%20UAE.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Move%20out%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20from%20Pakistan%20entirely%2C%20but%20the%20decision%20could%20see%20the%20PCB%20deciding%20to%20withdraw%20its%20team's%20participation%20from%20the%20tournament%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Postpone%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20indefinitely.%20This%20decision%20can%20have%20huge%20ramifications%20on%20the%20revenues%20of%20both%20the%20ICC%20and%20the%20PCB%2C%20who%20are%20all%20slated%20to%20earn%20big%20bucks%20from%20the%20tournament.%20The%20PCB%20has%20also%20been%20renovating%20its%20venues%20ahead%20of%20the%20tournament%2C%20incurring%20a%20significant%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20have%20hosted%20some%20of%20the%20top%20sides%20in%20the%20world%20on%20numerous%20occasions.%20So%20far%2C%20New%20Zealand%20have%20toured%20Pakistan%20thrice%2C%20England%20twice%2C%20and%20Australia%20once.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20PCB%20has%20also%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20ICC%20over%20BCCI's%20reluctance%20to%20send%20the%20Indian%20team%20to%20Pakistan%2C%20asking%20for%20the%20'real%20reason'%20behind%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20has%20responded%20to%20last%20week's%20ICC%20letter%20seeking%20clarifications%20for%20the%20BCCI's%20decision%20not%20to%20travel%20to%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%2C%26quot%3B%20PCB%20spokesperson%20Sami-Ul-Hasan%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cricbuzz.com%2Fcricket-news%2F132398%2Ficc-in-a-catch-22-situation-amid-pcbs-steadfast-stance-on-hosting-champions-trophy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECricbuzz%20%3C%2Fa%3Eon%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20learned%20that%20the%20PCB%20has%20been%20informed%20by%20Pakistan's%20government%20that%20the%20hybrid%20model%20is%20%26quot%3Boff%20the%20table%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1731596700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fi9tnj388_rohit-babar_625x300_13_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fchampions-trophy-controversy-pcb-vs-bcci-battle-leaves-icc-with-only-3-options-to-choose-from-7009449%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20is%20in%20a%20catch-22%20situation%20over%20next%20year's%20ICC%20Champions%20Trophy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fchampions-trophy-controversy-pcb-vs-bcci-battle-leaves-icc-with-only-3-options-to-choose-from-7009449%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hero%20MotoCorp%20Q2%20results%3A%20PAT%20rises%206%25%20to%20Rs%201%2C066%20crore%20on%20higher%20sales%22