rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F328099%2Fpunjab-man-in-faridkot-plants-trees-and-mud-nests-for-indigenous-birds%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enest%20conservation%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20agricultural%20background%20in%20a%20small%20village%20near%20Bengaluru%2C%20Ganeshan%20D%20has%20always%20held%20a%20deep%20love%20for%20nature%2C%20which%20evolved%20into%20a%20passionate%20commitment%20to%20environmental%20conservation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaneshan%E2%80%99s%20journey%20is%20rooted%20in%20a%20solid%20foundation%20of%20education%2C%20professional%20experience%2C%20and%20a%20deep%20commitment%20to%20giving%20back%20to%20nature.%20He%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20unique%20path%2C%20dedicating%20himself%20to%20making%20a%20meaningful%20impact%20through%20conservation%20efforts%2C%20with%20a%20particular%20focus%20on%20sparrow%20preservation%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewater%20manageme%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F336408%2Fchennai-floods-solution-to-groundwater-restoration-rainwater-harvesting-ancient-system-tamil-nadu%2F%5C%22%3Ent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20waste%20reduction.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20interest%20in%20nature%20began%20in%20his%20early%20years.%20%E2%80%9CFrom%20childhood%2C%20I%20have%20always%20been%20fascinated%20by%20nature%20and%20deeply%20passionate%20about%20conserving%20sparrows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganeshan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20As%20a%20student%2C%20his%20curiosity%20was%20nurtured%20by%20a%20supportive%20professor%20who%20recognised%20his%20zeal%20for%20the%20environment%20and%20encouraged%20him%20to%20pursue%20it%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20engineer%20to%20environment%20warrior%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGaneshan%20pursued%20mechanical%20engineering%2C%20earning%20a%20bachelor%E2%80%99s%20and%20master%E2%80%99s%20degree.%20Following%20his%20studies%2C%20he%20worked%20as%20a%20professor%20at%20SRM%20University%2C%20where%20he%20continued%20to%20foster%20his%20interests%20in%20the%20environment%20while%20also%20teaching.%20However%2C%20his%20professional%20life%20didn%E2%80%99t%20fully%20satisfy%20his%20passion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20time%20as%20a%20professor%2C%20he%20transitioned%20to%20the%20IT%20sector%2C%20currently%20working%20as%20a%20domain%20specialist%20in%20data%20technology%20at%20Coda%20Technology%20Solutions.%20Despite%20his%20technical%20career%2C%20his%20true%20calling%20lay%20in%20his%20environmental%20efforts%2C%20and%20thus%20the%20Koodugal%20Nest%20was%20born.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20sparrows%20enjoy%20the%20comfort%20of%20one%20of%20Koodugal%20Nest's%20boxes%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FIMG-20200416-WA0001-1-1731592014-768x512.jpg%2