front.%20His%20first%20major%20success%20was%20the%20band%20%3Cem%3ERaitila%20Rajasthan%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20comprising%20seven%20to%20eight%20young%20men%20from%20folk%20music%20backgrounds.%20They%20trained%20and%20rehearsed%20for%20about%20six%20months%2C%20resulting%20in%20their%20debut%20song%20%3Cem%3EMehman%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20which%20was%20composed%20and%20arranged%20by%20Bhati%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20track%20gained%20immense%20popularity%2C%20even%20being%20featured%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20the%20popular%20Netflix%20show%20%3Cem%3EMismatched%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20where%20it%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20next%20project%20%3Cem%3EKaisariya%20Rajasthan%20%3C%2Fem%3Ereceived%20similar%20response.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20basically%20created%20bands%20and%20albums%20that%20have%20their%20own%20identity%2C%20not%20just%20that%20of%20folk%20music%20but%20of%20true%20Rajasthani%20artists%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203672px)%20100vw%2C%203672px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Musicians%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20Langa%2C%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20Manganiyar%20communities%20unite%20on%20stage%2C%20sharing%20the%20soul%20of%20folk%20music%20with%20a%20captivated%20audience.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098.jpg%203672w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FTCH03359_11zon-1731069098-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375566%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20make%20people%20realise%20that%20these%20artists%20are%20worth%20the%20money%20and%20time%20just%20as%20much%20as%20others%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20how%20folk%20artists%20have%20not%20been%20given%20their%20due%20diligence%20in%20a%20long%20time%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20certain%20perception%20people%20have%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20folk%20artists.%20If%20you%20go%20to%20an%20event%20organiser%20and%20say%20you%20have%20some%20folk%20artists%20who%E2%80%99d%20love%20to%20perform%2C%20the%20artist%20fee%20immediately%20cuts%20in%20half%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20the%20funds%20are%20coming%20from%20a%20private%20organisation%20or%20the%20Government.%20What%20we%20wanted%20was%20to%20make%20people%20realise%20that%20these%20artists%20are%20worth%20the%20money%20and%20time%20just%20as%20much%20as%20others%20are%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20these%20initial%20projects%20gained%20enough%20traction%2C%20Bhati%20and%20his%20team%20kept%20meeting%20new%20people%20and%20patrons%20who%20wanted%20to%20help.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20we%20got%20our%20footing%20right%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20for%20these%20artists%E2%80%99%20development%20also.%20So%2C%20we%20started%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEducating%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artists%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202023%2C%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20fully%20funded%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F365250%2Fvinyasa-earth-sankalp-sharma-sustainable-homestay-jaipur-artist-residencies-mud-bamboo-cob-lime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eartist%20residency%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhere%20young%20children%20from%20across%20Rajasthan%20can%20gather%20to%20learn%20folk%20music%20from%20maestros%20and%20gurus.%20This%20initiative%20is%20groundbreaking%20because%2C%20unlike%20Indian%20classical%20music%2C%20there%20is%20no%20formal%20educational%20structure%20for%20folk%20music.%20Traditionally%2C%20it%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20orally%20through%20generations%2C%20with%20no%20written%20records%20to%20preserve%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residency%20spans%20seven%20days%20and%20includes%20nine%20classes%20covering%20various%20disciplines%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20vocals%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekamaicha%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Emurli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flute)%2C%20%3Cem%3Etandura%20%3C%2Fem%3E(tamboura)%2C%20and%20more.%20Currently%2C%20the%20programme%20works%20with%20three%20folk%20music%20communities%3A%20%3Cem%3ELanga%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3EMeghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3EManganiyars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20allowing%20students%20to%20learn%20directly%20from%20master%20artists%20of%20these%20traditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20dignitaries%20like%20Lakha%20Khan%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20Padma%20Shri%20awardee%20and%20the%20maestro%20of%20Sarangi%2C%20give%20masterclasses%20here.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20go%20to%20foreign%20countries%20or%20even%20other%20states%20to%20play%2C%20the%20reception%20is%20good%20because%20the%20type%20of%20people%20who%20come%20to%20watch%20us%20actually%20value%20folk%20singing.%20So%2C%20people%20do%20like%20it.%20But%20it%20is%20important%20to%20actually%20teach%20kids%20and%20make%20them%20understand%20what%20it%20means%20because%20only%20then%20will%20this%20art%20be%20able%20to%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%203269px)%20100vw%2C%203269px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%223269%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20from%20the%20Langa%2C%20Meghwal%2C%20and%20Manganiyar%20communities%20learning%20Rajasthani%20folk%20music%20directly%20from%20master%20artists%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201.jpg%203269w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-IMG_8789-1_11zon-1731069201-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375568%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222179%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%2C%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20residency%20also%20promotes%20community%20building%2C%20addressing%20the%20longstanding%20divisions%20between%20different%20folk%20music%20communities.%20Traditionally%2C%20these%20groups%20rarely%20interact%20or%20share%20performance%20spaces%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20palpable%20sense%20of%20hostility.%20However%2C%20by%20bringing%20the%20younger%20generation%20together%20in%20a%20shared%20learning%20environment%2C%20the%20programme%20helps%20break%20down%20these%20barriers%2C%20fostering%20mutual%20respect%20and%20collaboration%20as%20they%20freely%20interact%20and%20learn%20from%20one%20another.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20in%20the%20day%2C%20in%20our%20villages%2C%20artists%20would%20interact%20with%20each%20other%20at%20cultural%20events%20and%20weddings%2C%20where%20they%20would%20get%20to%20play%20night%20after%20night.%20But%20that%20system%20has%20ended%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20residency%20took%20place%20in%20Pokhran%2C%20with%20support%20from%20BlueCity%20Walls%2C%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20and%20some%20anonymous%20funders.%20Speaking%20with%20Rakshat%20Hooja%2C%20the%20current%20head%20of%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%2C%20he%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20%3Cem%3ERajasthani%20%3C%2Fem%3Efolk%20music%20is%20thriving%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20established%20artists%20who%20get%20booked%20for%20the%20entire%20year%20and%20travel%20extensively.%20For%20newcomers%2C%20however%2C%20breaking%20into%20that%20field%20remains%20a%20challenge.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jaipur%20Virasat%20Foundation%20%E2%80%94%20which%20focuses%20on%20the%20social%20and%20cultural%20development%20of%20Rajasthan%20%E2%80%94%20provided%20Bhati%20and%20Sharon%20with%20valuable%20guidance%2C%20support%2C%20and%20assistance%20in%20raising%20funds%20for%20their%20initiatives.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20idea%20falls%20in%20line%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20we%20do.%20And%20it%20was%20lovely%20to%20see%20these%20senior%20artists%20come%20and%20mentor%20young%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rakshat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20first%20year%2C%20%3Cem%3ELok%20Sangeet%20Shala%3C%2Fem%3E%20welcomed%20around%2050%20children%2C%20ages%2012%20to%2018.%20This%20year%2C%20the%20number%20grew%20to%2078%2C%20which%20included%2010%20girls%20from%20the%20%3Cem%3EMeghwal%3C%2Fem%3E%20community%20and%20participants%20from%20outside%20the%20traditional%20folk%20music%20communities.%20Both%20of%20these%20are%20as%20rare%20as%20a%20cool%20afternoon%20in%20Jaisalmer%20during%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20women%20and%20healing%20communities%20through%20folk%20music%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%202024%2C%20Jodhpur%E2%80%99s%20JIET%20University%20representatives%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20present%20at%20the%20previous%20year%E2%80%99s%20showing%20%E2%80%94%20opened%20their%20hearts%20and%20the%20entire%20campus%20to%20provide%20space%20to%20these%20artists.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20time%2C%20we%20organised%20the%20residency%20on%20their%20campus%2C%20where%20students%20practised%20in%20the%20central%20garden%2C%20right%20in%20front%20of%20the%20hospital.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20even%20patients%20could%20enjoy%20the%20music%2C%20creating%20a%20unique%20atmosphere%20of%20healing%20and%20cultural%20exchange%2C%E2%80%9D%20Bhati%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20shares%20touching%20stories%2C%20like%20one%20where%20a%20son%2C%20while%20waiting%20for%20his%20father%20who%20was%20undergoing%20chemotherapy%2C%20sat%20and%20watched%20the%20students%20play%2C%20enjoying%20the%20music.%20It%E2%80%99s%20moments%20like%20these%20that%2C%20without%20a%20doubt%2C%20help%20people%20navigate%20the%20challenges%20of%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%204569px)%20100vw%2C%204569px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%224569%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Young%20women%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20communities%20performing%20together%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency%2C%20showcasing%20their%20talent%20and%20confidence%20in%20a%20supportive%20and%20trusting%20environment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265.jpg%204569w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-2048x1365.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-1200x800.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FCopy-of-DEV09823_11zon-1731069265-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-375571%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223046%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EYoung%20women%20from%20Rajasthan%E2%80%99s%20folk%20music%20communities%20confidently%20participate%20in%20the%20residency.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20these%20traditional%20communities%2C%20women%20have%20often%20been%20sidelined%20and%20discouraged%20from%20taking%20centre%20stage.%20However%2C%20Bhati%E2%80%99s%20work%20has%20begun%20to%20shift%20that%20perception%2C%20even%20if%20just%20a%20little.%20For%20example%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20worked%20with%20Ganga%20and%20Sundar%2C%20a%20mother-daughter%20duo.%20To%20see%20a%20young%20woman%20who%20once%20lacked%20confidence%20and%20had%20never%20sung%20outside%20her%20home%20now%20performing%20at%20shows%20and%20private%20events%20is%20the%20biggest%20reward%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20speaking%20with%20Ganga%2C%20who%20is%20as%20sweet%20in%20conversation%20as%20she%20is%20bold%20in%20song%2C%20she%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20come%20from%20a%20family%20of%20musicians%2C%20and%20I%20learned%20singing%20from%20my%20mother%20and%20grandmother.%20But%20I%20never%20thought%20I%20could%20reach%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20reassuring%20to%20see%20young%20women%20participate%20in%20our%20residency%2C%20to%20the%20point%20where%20their%20parents%20trust%20us%20enough%20to%20let%20them%20attend%20without%20accompaniment%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Bhati.%20This%20trust%20is%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20strong%20relationships%20they%E2%80%99ve%20built%20within%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EKeeping%20the%20music%20alive%3A%20Supporting%20artists%20through%20the%20pandemic%20and%20beyond%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20folk%20artists%2C%20their%20livelihood%20depends%20entirely%20on%20their%20ability%20to%20perform%2C%20but%20during%20the%20COVID%20lockdown%2C%20when%20they%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20take%20the%20stage%2C%20the%20impact%20was%20devastating%20for%20entire%20communities.%20To%20support%20them%2C%20Sharon%20facilitated%20a%20collaboration%20with%20My%20Mensa%2C%20a%20visual%20learning%20app%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300577%2Fbest-folk-artists-and-artisans-take-masterclasses-on-first-culture-tech-platform-memeraki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20offering%20these%20artists%20opportunities%20%3C%2Fa%3Efor%20live%20music%20sessions.%20This%20initiative%20ensured%20that%20the%20artists%20were%20fairly%20compensated%2C%20while%20also%20driving%20increased%20app%20traffic%20and%20downloads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20had%20to%20sit%20at%20home%20and%20do%20some%20of%20the%20work%2C%20so%20we%20were%20fine%20doing%20it%20for%20free%2C%20but%20the%20artists%20needed%20to%20be%20paid%20%E2%80%94%20that%20was%20our%20only%20condition%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Bhati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20peak%20months%20of%20COVID-19%2C%20they%20successfully%20hosted%20live%20sessions%20on%20the%20app%2C%20allowing%20every%20participating%20artist%20to%20receive%20compensation.%20This%20initiative%20also%20encouraged%20greater%20involvement%20from%20women%2C%20as%20it%20eliminated%20the%20need%20for%20them%20to%20travel%2C%20enabling%20those%20who%20had%20only%20sung%20for%20their%20families%20to%20showcase%20their%20talent%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202448px)%20100vw%2C%202448px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222448%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20experienced%20Rajasthani%20folk%20artist%20teaching%20young%20children%20the%20intricacies%20of%20traditional%20music%20at%20the%20Lok%20Sangeet%20Shala%20residency%2C%20promoting%20cultural%20preservation%20and%20knowledge%20transfer.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846.jpg%202448w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FLSS-2018-1-1_11zon-1731068846-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.the