0AcadBoost%2C%20which%20focuses%20on%20online%20education%2C%20software%2C%20and%20email%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20his%20entrepreneurial%20ventures%2C%20Kalpit%20is%20an%20active%20mentor%20and%20advisor%20to%20several%20startups%2C%20helping%20students%20and%20young%20professionals%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F332971%2Fbrillio-national-stem-learning-challenge-government-schools-rural-india-science-labs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeducational%20and%20career%20pursuits%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Through%20his%20platform%2C%20he%20also%20shares%20valuable%20content%20on%20exam%20preparation%2C%20business%20growth%2C%20and%20career-building%20strategies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEssential%20advice%20for%20JEE%20aspirants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20practical%20and%20insightful%20tips%20from%20Kalpit%20Veerwal%20that%20he%20believes%20are%20essential%20for%20cracking%20the%20JEE%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Build%20consistency%20in%20study%20routine%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20first%20piece%20of%20advice%20I%E2%80%99d%20give%20is%20to%20be%20consistent%20in%20your%20studies%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kalpit%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%20He%20stresses%20that%20consistent%20study%20is%20more%20effective%20than%20short%2C%20intense%20bursts%20of%20effort.%20According%20to%20him%2C%20students%20who%20study%20regularly%2C%20even%20for%20three%20to%20four%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20tend%20to%20outperform%20those%20who%20alternate%20between%20intense%20study%20sessions%20and%20periods%20of%20inactivity.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20sticking%20to%20a%20daily%20routine%20to%20steadily%20build%20your%20knowledge%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cla