D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Manage%20soil%20pH%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECold%20temperatures%20and%20winter%20rains%20can%20increase%20soil%20acidity%20in%20high-rainfall%20areas%20like%20the%20Western%20Ghats%20(in%20Kerala%20and%20Karnataka)%20and%20the%20Northeast%20(in%20Assam).%20Increased%20acidity%20can%20affect%20nutrient%20retention%2C%20making%20it%20more%20challenging%20to%20grow%20crops%20like%20rice%2C%20soybean%2C%20and%20cotton.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20neutralise%20acidity%2C%20farmers%20should%20test%20soil%20pH%20regularly%20and%20apply%20lime%20or%20dolomite%20to%20restore%20a%20more%20neutral%20environment%20suitable%20for%20a%20range%20of%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Control%20erosion%20with%20terracing%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeavy%20rains%20in%20winter%2C%20particularly%20in%20hilly%20regions%20like%20the%20Himalayas%2C%20Sikkim%2C%20and%20parts%20of%20Uttarakhand%2C%20can%20lead%20to%20increased%20soil%20erosion%2C%20washing%20away%20valuable%20topsoil.%20This%20can%20negatively%20affect%20crops%20such%20as%20tea%2C%20coffee%2C%20and%20rice%2C%20which%20are%20often%20grown%20on%20slopes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20soil%20erosion%2C%20farmers%20should%20adopt%20practices%20like%20terracing%2C%20contour%20farming%2C%20and%20planting%20cover%20crops%20such%20as%20barley%20or%20gram%2C%20which%20can%20help%20stabilise%20soil%20and%20protect%20it%20from%20water%20runoff.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201575px)%20100vw%2C%201575px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fcontour_11zon-1730882654.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221575%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20scenic%20view%20of%20contour%20terrace%20farming%20on%20a%20hilly%20landscape%2C%20with%20neatly%20arranged%20terraces%20of%20crops%20such%20as%20barley%20or%20wheat%2C%20designed%20to%20prevent%20soil%20er